Highlighted by a sophisticated suite of advanced technologies, this E-Class delivers unparalleled driving dynamics and exceptional comfort. Enjoy the convenience of the COMAND navigation system, the enhanced visibility of the 360° view parking camera, and the added safety of blind spot warning and lane departure prevention systems. The sport-tuned suspension and upgraded wheels provide a thrilling and responsive driving experience, while the premium audio system and Apple CarPlay/Android Auto integration ensure you're always connected and entertained.

Whether you're commuting in style, embarking on a road trip, or seeking an unparalleled driving experience, this 2019 Mercedes-Benz E-Class E 53 AMG® 4MATIC® is the perfect choice. With low mileage and a wealth of premium features, this exceptional vehicle is a true testament to Mercedes-Benz's commitment to excellence.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2019 Mercedes-Benz S-Class S 560 4MATIC®. This meticulously maintained luxury sedan boasts a striking White exterior, complemented by a suite of premium features that redefine the art of automotive excellence.

Indulge in the unparalleled comfort and convenience of this S-Class, which comes equipped with an impressive array of carefully curated amenities:

• AMG® Line Exterior
• Driver Assistance Package
• KEYLESS GO® Comfort Package
• Premium Package
• Sport Package Code
• Warmth & Comfort Package

Slip into the driver's seat and immerse yourself in the refined ambiance of the cabin, where Heated & Active Ventilated Rear Seats, Power Rear Seats, and a Rear Memory Seats provide unmatched personalization. The 3-Spoke Wood & Leather Steering Wheel and KEYLESS GO® technology offer effortless control, while the Power Moonroof: Panorama and Surround View Camera enhance your driving experience.

Powered by a robust 4.0L V8 engine paired with a 9-Speed Automatic transmission and 4MATIC® all-wheel drive, this S-Class delivers a captivating blend of performance and efficiency, with a city MPG of 17 and a highway MPG of 27.

Safety and technology take center stage, with features like Active Distance Assist DISTRONIC®, Active Steering Assist, Apple CarPlay®/Android Auto®, and a Burmester® Surround Sound System. The comprehensive Driver Assistance Package and Warmth & Comfort Package elevate your driving experience, providing a level of sophistication and convenience that is truly unparalleled.

Discover the true essence of luxury and performance in this exceptional 2019 Mercedes-Benz S-Class S 560 4MATIC®. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident that this remarkable vehicle will captivate your senses and exceed your expectations.

description: Experience Scandinavian luxury and adventure with this 2025 Volvo V60 Cross Country AWD B5 Plus. With advanced AWD, a powerful 2.0L Turbo I4 engine, and an 8-speed shiftable automatic transmission, this wagon is built for confident driving in any condition. Enjoy cutting-edge technology like Google Built-In infotainment, Apple CarPlay/Android Auto, an intuitive navigation system with over-the-air updates, and a panoramic moonroof. Safety is paramount with features such as Head-on Collision Avoidance, Front and Rear Pedestrian Automatic Emergency Braking, Lane Keeping Assist with Blind Spot Integration, Rear Cross Traffic Alert, and a Surround View Camera. Relax in leather upholstery, with heated front seats, power-adjustable options, and a sophisticated interior featuring wood and alloy trim. Practical details like a sensor-activated power liftgate, 19-inch alloy wheels, and roof rails make this V60 ready for your next journey. Discover refined versatility and Volvo's renowned safety in a stylish, capable wagon. Visit our dealership in northwest Austin! Reach us at 512-620-8000 Monday through Saturday 9 am to 7 pm or email/chat with us on VolvoHillCountry.com anytime. Volvo Cars Hill Country inventory changes daily so be sure to check back often. Take advantage of our excellent deals today! While we make every effort to present accurate information, we cannot guarantee a vehicle is still available based on a listing. Experience adventure in this low-mileage 2025 Subaru Outback AWD Premium, finished in classic white with only 4,127 miles on the odometer. This crossover blends reliability, comfort, and advanced technology, making it the perfect companion for both city commutes and weekend getaways. Key features include Subaru's Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive, heated front seats, adaptive cruise control with lane centering, and a power-adjustable driver's seat for ultimate comfort. Stay connected with the STARLINK infotainment system featuring an 11.6-inch touchscreen, wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, plus SiriusXM Satellite Radio. Enjoy added convenience with keyless entry, a power rear liftgate, and roof rails for extra cargo. This Outback also offers LED headlights and fog lights for enhanced visibility. With its rugged capability, impressive safety suite, and tech-forward interior, this Outback is ready for your next journey. Discover the perfect blend of luxury, versatility, and performance with this Certified 2025 Volvo V60 Cross Country B5 Plus AWD, finished in elegant Silver Dawn Metallic. Recently arrived at Autobahn Volvo in Fort Worth, this sophisticated wagon delivers the unmistakable Scandinavian design, cutting-edge safety technology, and refined driving dynamics that Volvo is known for. With market-based pricing, you can feel confident knowing this vehicle is competitively priced within current market conditions, giving you exceptional value on a premium luxury vehicle.

Originally priced at $53,045, this V60 Cross Country has only 19,392 miles, offering a nearly-new driving experience with extremely low mileage. Powered by a 2.0L turbocharged I4 engine paired with AWD and an Automatic transmission with Geartronic, it delivers smooth, responsive acceleration, confident handling, and all-weather capability. This versatile wagon achieves 24 MPG city/31 MPG highway, making it practical for daily commuting, long road trips, and everything in between.

The B5 Plus trim elevates comfort and convenience with premium features that enhance both driver and passenger experience. The cabin is equipped with a Climate Package to ensure perfect temperature control year-round, heated rear seats, and a heated steering wheel for ultimate comfort in colder conditions. The V60 Cross Country's interior combines functional luxury with intuitive technology, providing an environment that is both welcoming and practical. The stylish 19" 5-Double Spoke Diamond-Cut Alloy wheels add a bold presence while complementing the sleek exterior lines of this capable wagon.

As a Volvo Certified Pre-Owned vehicle, this V60 Cross Country comes with a comprehensive suite of benefits that provide peace of mind for years to come. Every Certified Volvo undergoes a rigorous 170+ point inspection to ensure mechanical reliability and aesthetic quality, and includes extensive coverage and perks:

* 12-Month/Unlimited-Mile Certified Limited Warranty, upgradeable up to 5 years and unlimited miles

* $0 deductible

* Transferable warranty

* Roadside Assistance

* Vehicle History Report with Buyback Guarantee

* 1-Year complimentary Volvo On Call app, providing remote climate control, locking/unlocking, fuel level, maintenance reminders, and a driving journal

* 8-Year/100,000-Mile Battery Warranty for Certified fully electric and plug-in hybrid Volvo vehicles

This V60 Cross Country B5 Plus AWD offers a versatile driving experience that seamlessly blends the practicality of a wagon with the refinement of a luxury SUV. Its advanced driver-assistance technologies, responsive handling, and spacious, thoughtfully designed interior make it ideal for families, professionals, and adventure-seekers alike. Whether navigating city streets, tackling highways, or exploring scenic backroads, this V60 provides the confidence, safety, and comfort you expect from Volvo.

At Autobahn Volvo in Fort Worth, we offer a wide variety of premium vehicles, including numerous Certified Pre-Owned Volvo models, making it easy to find the vehicle that fits your lifestyle and budget. Serving drivers from Fort Worth, Weatherford, Burleson, Flower Mound, and Arlington, TX, our dealership also provides nationwide delivery for added convenience.

Call (817) 390-3236 today to speak with one of our knowledgeable sales associates or to schedule a virtual walkaround. Explore the sleek exterior, premium interior, and advanced features of this 2025 Volvo V60 Cross Country B5 Plus AWD from the comfort of your own home. Don't miss your chance to own a nearly-new Certified Volvo wagon with low mileage, high-value features, and the confidence of Volvo Certification-available now at Autobahn Volvo.

description: This 2024 Subaru Outback AWD Premium has 9,315 miles, a clean CarFax history, and one previous owner. With such low mileage, it presents as a nearly new crossover that offers Subarus signature reliability, safety, and all-weather capability. The standard all-wheel-drive system provides excellent traction and stability in a wide range of driving conditions, making it a great choice for daily commuting, road trips, and outdoor adventures. Under the hood, the Outback is powered by a responsive four-cylinder engine paired with a smooth continuously variable automatic transmission. This powertrain delivers a balanced mix of performance and fuel efficiency, providing confident acceleration and a comfortable driving experience. The suspension is tuned for a smooth ride while still offering stability and control on highways and uneven road surfaces. Inside, the Premium trim offers a comfortable and well-equipped cabin with thoughtful features throughout. The interior includes high-quality materials, supportive seating, and a clean, modern layout. A large touchscreen infotainment system anchors the dashboard and provides easy access to navigation, media, and vehicle settings. Smartphone integration with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto comes standard, keeping drivers connected on the go. Passenger space is generous in both the front and rear seats, making long drives comfortable for everyone. Cargo space is also a strong point of the Outback, with a wide and versatile rear cargo area that easily accommodates luggage, groceries, or outdoor gear. The rear seats fold flat to expand the cargo area even further, adding to the vehicles practicality. Safety is a core strength of the Outback, with Subarus EyeSight driver assistance technology included. Features such as adaptive cruise control, lane centering, automatic emergency braking, and pre-collision braking work together to enhance driver awareness and confidence on the road. In summary, this 2024 Subaru Outback AWD Premium with 9,315 miles, a clean CarFax report, and one owner offers an outstanding combination of low mileage, modern features, and all-wheel-drive capability. It is an excellent choice for anyone seeking a reliable, comfortable, and versatile vehicle with like-new condition and strong long-term value.

Vehicle Details
Looking for a stylish, practical compact crossover with excellent fuel economy and modern tech? This 2022 Kia Soul LX in Enterprise, AL is the perfect match. With just 37,267 miles, front-wheel drive, and a dependable 2.0L 4-cylinder gasoline engine, this Kia Soul delivers reliable daily commuting and confident highway performance. The comfortable interior, roomy cargo area, and upright design make getting in and out and loading gear effortless. Tech-savvy drivers will appreciate the seamless smartphone integration via Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, plus the handy Back-Up Camera that makes parking and reversing safer and simpler. Advanced safety features include Collision Avoidance systems to help protect you and your passengers. This vehicle also carries a CARFAX Clean Report, giving you extra peace of mind about its history. You'll enjoy low running costs, straightforward maintenance, and thoughtful Kia engineering that emphasizes comfort and durability. Whether you're driving around town in Enterprise or taking weekend trips, the 2022 Kia Soul LX balances practicality with personality. Priced to move, this Kia Soul offers the best price in the area—an exceptional value for a late-model, low-mileage compact SUV with desirable equipment. Act quickly to secure this clean, well-equipped 2022 Kia Soul LX with modern connectivity and safety features. Contact us to schedule a test drive and experience why this Kia Soul stands out as a smart, budget-friendly choice.

Equipment
The Kia Soul comes equipped with Android Auto for seamless smartphone integration on the road. The vehicle features a hands-free Bluetooth phone system. See what's behind you with the back up camera on it. It employs advanced tech for collision avoidance, enhancing safety on the road. The vehicle offers Apple CarPlay for seamless connectivity. This model has a clean CARFAX vehicle history report. This model projects refinement with a racy metallic gray exterior. Set the temperature exactly where you are most comfortable in this small suv. The fan speed and temperature will automatically adjust to maintain your preferred zone climate. It has a 4 Cyl, 2.0L high output engine. This model is front wheel drive. This vehicle is equipped with a gasoline engine. Light weight alloy wheels on this Kia Soul are the perfect compliment to a stylish body. The vehicle features cruise control for long trips. This 2022 Kia Soul has an automatic transmission.

Packages

Discover the ultimate heavy-duty pickup with the 2022 Ford F-350SD Lariat. This powerful and capable truck is packed with premium features that elevate your driving experience to new heights.

• Ford Gold Certified
• 7 Year/100k Powertrain Warranty
• 12 Month/12,000 Mile Comprehensive Warranty
• 20,000lbs Towing Capacity
• Power Stroke 6.7L V8 Diesel Turbocharged Engine
• Lariat Ultimate Package
• Pro Trailer Backup Assist
• Twin Panel Power Moonroof
• Chrome Package
• FX4 Off-Road Package
• Heavy-Service Front Suspension Package
• Heated Rear Seats
• Adaptive Cruise Control & Collision Warning
• 397 Amp Alternator
• Engine Block Heater
• 6" Angular Bright Polished Extended Running Boards

This F-350SD Lariat is more than just a workhorse – it's a premium, feature-packed truck that elevates your driving experience. The powerful 6.7L Power Stroke V8 Diesel engine provides exceptional towing and hauling capabilities, while the Lariat Ultimate Package adds a host of premium amenities like heated and ventilated front seats, a panoramic moonroof, and a premium audio system.

For enhanced off-road prowess, the FX4 Off-Road Package equips this F-350 with specialized suspension tuning, skid plates, and an electronic-locking rear differential. The Pro Trailer Backup Assist feature makes maneuvering a trailer a breeze, while the Ultimate Trailer Tow Camera System provides unparalleled visibility.

Comfort and convenience are also prioritized, with features like a heated steering wheel, rain-sensing windshield wipers, and a 360-degree camera system. The spacious and well-appointed cabin offers ample room for both passengers and cargo, making this F-350SD Lariat the ultimate choice for those who demand the best.

Ford Gold Certified vehicles undergo a rigorous 172-point inspection and come with a comprehensive warranty, providing you with the peace of mind you deserve. Additionally, you'll receive 22,000 FordPass Rewards Points to use towards your first two maintenance visits, ensuring your ownership experience is seamless.

For better peace of mind, all our used vehicles have a 127-point inspection and come with a 5-day return, 30-day exchange (As-Is vehicles are excluded). Our exclusive Auto Rewards Program provides better value with Free First Oil change, Free Pa State Safety inspections, discounts for local merchants and more. Plus, you can earn up to $2000 towards your next vehicle just by servicing with Fred Beans! As Fred Beans always says, our used cars are better because our reputation depends on it.

Don't miss the opportunity to experience the unparalleled capabilities and premium features of the 2022 Ford F-350SD Lariat. Visit our showroom today and let us help you discover the ultimate heavy-duty pickup that will exceed your every expectation.

description:
2023 Subaru Outback Limited Certified Pre-Owned - AWD, 2.5L H-4, panoramic moonroof, heated leather fronts, navigation/Premium Audio, CarPlay/Android Auto, 26/32 MPG.

AWD | 2.5L H-4 | CVT w/dual shift mode | 26/32 MPG | Panoramic sun/moonroof | Heated front seats | Heated steering wheel | Leather seating surfaces | 10-way power driver seat w/memory & lumbar | Power passenger seat | Navigation & Premium Sound | Apple CarPlay & Android Auto | Wi-Fi hotspot & telematics | Hands-free power liftgate | Back-up camera | Blind spot monitor | Adaptive cruise w/lane keep & Evasion Assist | LED headlights w/Auto High Beam | Heated mirrors w/turn signals | Universal garage door opener

CPO benefits

152-point inspection | 7yr/100,000mi powertrain from original in-service date | $0 deductible | roadside assistance | vehicle history | transferable warranty | SiriusXM 3-month trial | STARLINK 1-year trial

Performance

Symmetrical AWD and a 2.5L H-4 deliver surefooted traction and smooth, quiet power in all seasons. The CVTs dual-shift logic helps keep revs low and fuel economy high at 26/32 MPG.

Comfort & Convenience

Heated leather front seats, a power driver seat with memory and lumbar, and dual-zone climate ease daily commutes. A hands-free power liftgate and keyless access with push-button start simplify loading and go.

Technology

Built-in navigation and the Premium Sound System make road trips easier and music crisp. Apple CarPlay/Android Auto, Wi-Fi hotspot, telematics, and a trip computer keep you connected and informed.

Safety

Blind Spot Monitor and Rear Cross-Traffic alerts assist with merging and backing. Adaptive Cruise Control with Lane Keep, Driver Monitoring, Front Collision Mitigation, and a full airbag suite add confidence.

Exterior & Interior

Magnetite Gray Metallic pairs with LED headlights, Auto High Beam, fog lamps, and heated turn-signal mirrors for visibility. Panoramic moonroof, aluminum wheels, roof rails, privacy glass, and a rear spoiler add style and utility.

Driving Experience

Calm, composed, and surefooted, it tracks confidently over rough pavement and winter roads.

History Summary

Certified Pre-Owned. No Open Recalls. Sold as a Subaru Certified Pre-Owned Vehicle.

description:
This 2023 Kia Soul LX is a distinctive compact hatchback that blends practicality, efficiency, and a bold design into a vehicle that is easy to drive and economical to own. With 60,124 miles, this Soul has been appropriately used for its model year and remains a strong option for buyers seeking dependable transportation with modern styling and everyday versatility. Finished in Steel Gray with a Black interior, it presents a clean, contemporary appearance that stands out while remaining professional and approachable.

The exterior design of the Kia Soul LX is instantly recognizable, featuring its boxy profile and upright stance that maximize interior space while maintaining a compact footprint. The Steel Gray exterior complements the Souls modern design, giving it a sleek and neutral look that works well in a variety of settings. Its four-door hatchback layout provides easy access for passengers and cargo, while the compact size makes it simple to maneuver through city streets and parking lots.

Inside, the Black interior offers a functional and comfortable cabin designed with usability in mind. The seating position is upright, providing excellent visibility for the driver and a confident feel behind the wheel. Seats are supportive and well suited for daily commuting, errands, or longer drives. The cabin layout is straightforward, with controls placed intuitively for ease of use and minimal distraction. Despite its compact exterior dimensions, the Soul makes excellent use of space, offering generous headroom and legroom for both front and rear passengers.

On the road, the front-wheel-drive configuration delivers predictable handling and stable performance in everyday driving conditions. The suspension is tuned for comfort, absorbing road imperfections while maintaining a composed ride. Steering is light and responsive, making the Soul easy to drive for a wide range of drivers. Its efficient performance helps keep fuel costs manageable, an important consideration for daily drivers and commuters.

Cargo versatility is one of the Souls strongest attributes. The rear hatch provides convenient access to a flexible cargo area that easily accommodates groceries, luggage, or everyday gear. Folding rear seats expand the cargo space further when needed, allowing the Soul to adapt to a variety of lifestyles and transportation needs.

Overall, this 2023 Kia Soul LX is an excellent choice for buyers looking for a reliable, efficient, and versatile compact vehicle with a unique personality. Its spacious interior, easy drivability, and proven design make it a smart option for commuters, students, or anyone seeking a practical hatchback that delivers consistent everyday value.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, technology, and efficiency with the 2023 Kia Soul LX. This captivating compact SUV is a true standout, offering a winning combination of features that cater to the modern driver's needs.

Boasting a sleek, eye-catching exterior in the Snow White Pearl color, the 2023 Kia Soul LX is a head-turner on the road. Its impressive list of features includes:

• Kia Certified
• Back-Up Camera

Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by a well-appointed cabin that prioritizes both comfort and convenience. Enjoy the convenience of Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, as well as the added safety of features like Steering Wheel Mounted Audio Controls, Exterior Parking Camera Rear, and Auto High-Beam Headlights.

Powered by a 2.0L I4 DOHC engine paired with a CVT transmission, the 2023 Kia Soul LX delivers an exceptional balance of performance and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 29 MPG in the city and 35 MPG on the highway. This FWD SUV is a true all-around performer, ready to tackle your daily commute or weekend adventures with ease.

As a Kia Certified Pre-Owned vehicle, this 2023 Soul LX comes with a comprehensive 165-point inspection, Roadside Assistance, and a transferable warranty that provides you with the peace of mind you deserve. Enjoy the benefits of a 12-month/12,000-mile "Platinum Coverage" limited warranty, as well as a 120-month/100,000-mile powertrain limited warranty from the original in-service date.

With its exceptional features, impressive performance, and the added assurance of Kia's renowned certification program, the 2023 Kia Soul LX is a compelling choice for the discerning driver. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by this exceptional compact SUV.

description:
Discover the exceptional 2023 Subaru Outback Limited XT, a versatile and well-equipped SUV that's ready to elevate your driving experience. With its sleek silver exterior, this Outback boasts a commanding presence on the road, complemented by its impressive 2.4L DOHC engine and Lineartronic CVT all-wheel-drive system.

• NO ACCIDENTS
• 1 OWNER
• LOCAL TRADE
• BLUETOOTH
• BACK-UP CAMERA
• MOONROOF/SUNROOF
• LEATHER
• PREMIUM SOUND
• HEATED SEATS
• POWER SEAT

The Outback Limited XT also comes equipped with our popular package, including features like auto-dimming exterior mirrors, splash guards, a rear seat back protector, all-weather floor liners, and a rear bumper cover. Plus, the included windshield sunshade adds an extra layer of convenience and comfort.

Beneath the surface, this Outback delivers exceptional performance, with an EPA-estimated 22 MPG in the city and 29 MPG on the highway. The 4-wheel independent suspension and speed-sensitive power steering ensure a smooth and responsive ride, while the 4-wheel disc brakes with ABS provide confident stopping power.

Step inside the Outback Limited XT, and you'll be greeted by a wealth of premium features, including a 11.6-inch Subaru STARLINK multimedia navigation system, a 12-speaker harman/kardon sound system, dual-zone automatic climate control, and a power driver's seat with memory settings. The perforated leather-trimmed upholstery and heated front and rear seats add an extra touch of luxury, while the power liftgate and rear-view camera make loading and unloading a breeze.

Safety is also a top priority in the Outback, with features like dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, a knee airbag, and an emergency communication system. The Subaru EyeSight driver assist technology, including auto high-beam headlights and a rear-view camera, further enhance your peace of mind on the road.

Don't miss your chance to experience the exceptional 2023 Subaru Outback Limited XT. Visit our showroom today and let our team of knowledgeable professionals guide you through this impressive SUV's features and capabilities. We're confident you'll be impressed by its combination of style, performance, and advanced technology.

Holz Motors - More than a better deal, a better dealership.

Enjoy the convenience of Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration, allowing you to seamlessly connect your smartphone and access your favorite apps and features. The 6.5J x 16" alloy wheels add a touch of sophistication to the exterior, while the woven and tricot cloth seat trim provides a premium feel.Whether you're commuting to the office, running errands, or embarking on a weekend getaway, this 2024 Kia Soul LX is the perfect companion. With its exceptional fuel efficiency, advanced safety features, and well-appointed interior, this vehicle is sure to exceed your expectations.We invite you to experience the joy of driving this exceptional Kia Soul LX. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this versatile SUV can elevate your daily driving experience. We're confident you'll be impressed by the value, quality, and performance this Soul LX has to offer.

description:
Crystal White Pearl 2018 Subaru Impreza 2.0i Premium AWD. This wellequipped Impreza offers excellent fuel economy, allwheeldrive confidence, and advanced Subaru technology, making it a strong fit for yearround driving in Spokane, Spokane Valley, Cheney, Airway Heights, and North Idaho. With Symmetrical AllWheel Drive, heated seats, and a comfortable, practical interior, it handles winter roads, steep hills, and changing weather across the Inland Northwest with ease.
Powered by a 2.0L 4cylinder DOHC engine paired with a Lineartronic CVT, the Impreza delivers reliable performance and outstanding fuel efficiency at 28/37 MPG City/Highway. Fourwheel independent suspension, traction control, stability control, and 4wheel disc brakes provide secure handling on snow, ice, and rain during Spokanes long winter season.
The Premium trim includes heated front bucket seats, cloth upholstery, heated mirrors, front center armrest, illuminated entry, front reading lights, rear seat splitfolding capability, roof rails, rear bumper applique, splash guards, and a cargo tray for added practicality. This layout offers a flexible interior ideal for commuting, outdoor activities, and weekend travel around the region.
Technology features include the Subaru STARLINK 6.5-inch Multimedia System, Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, AM/FM radio, Bluetooth connectivity, radio data system, steeringwheel mounted audio controls, and a trip computer. Additional convenience features include power windows, power steering, remote keyless entry, and fully automatic headlights.
Safety features include a rearview camera, STARLINK emergency communication capability, dual front and side airbags, knee airbag, occupant sensing airbag, electronic stability control, traction control, antiwhiplash head restraints, low tire pressure monitoring system, and variably intermittent wipers. Exterior features include heated power mirrors, fog lights, bodycolor bumpers, rear spoiler, roof rails, and 16-inch alloy wheels.
The 2018 Subaru Impreza is widely recognized for value and reliability, earning awards such as the ALG Residual Value Award, KBB Best Resale Value, KBB 10 Most Awarded Cars, KBB 10 Coolest New Cars Under $20,000, KBB 10 Best AWD Vehicles Under $25,000, and KBB Brand Image Awards.
This 2018 Subaru Impreza 2.0i Premium AWD delivers efficiency, capability, and allseason dependabilityideal for commuting, travel, and winter driving throughout the Spokane region.

description: 2018 Kia Soul + — Black exterior / Black interior Overview This 2018 Kia Soul + pairs a responsive 2.0L inline-4 engine (161 hp, 150 lb-ft torque) with an efficient drivetrain engineered for everyday driving. EPA-rated at 25 MPG city and 30 MPG highway, the Soul + balances practical fuel economy with confident low- and mid-range performance, making it well suited for urban commuting and highway cruising. Powertrain & Driving - 2.0L I4 engine delivering 161 horsepower and 150 lb-ft of torque for smooth, predictable acceleration - Tuned for a comfortable ride and composed handling, with an emphasis on efficiency and drivability - EPA fuel economy: 25 MPG city / 30 MPG highway Exterior - Classic black exterior paint that highlights the Soul’s distinctive, upright profile - Factory-equipped alloy wheels and a purposeful stance that combine style and everyday practicality - Integrated daytime running lights and front fog lamps help improve visibility in varying conditions - Functional rear hatch design for easy cargo access Interior & Comfort - Black interior with durable seating surfaces and a modern, driver-focused cockpit - Supportive front seats with manual adjustments, heated front seats available on factory-equipped packages - Thoughtful storage solutions throughout the cabin and a flexible 60/40-split rear seat for expanded cargo versatility - Automatic climate control and filtered ventilation for a comfortable cabin environment Infotainment & Connectivity - Factory touchscreen infotainment system with Bluetooth hands-free calling and audio streaming - USB and auxiliary inputs for device connectivity and charging - Smartphone integration support (Apple CarPlay and Android Auto) for navigation, messaging, and media via the center display - Steering-wheel-mounted audio and phone controls for safer, convenient operation while driving - Rearview camera to assist with parking and reversing maneuvers Safety & Driver Assistance - Comprehensive passive and active safety equipment including multiple airbags (front, side and curtain) and front-seat knee airbag - Anti-lock braking system (ABS), electronic stability control (ESC) and traction control to help maintain control in challenging conditions - Tire pressure monitoring system (TPMS) and LATCH anchors for safe child-seat installation - Available driver convenience technologies designed to enhance everyday safety and confidence Convenience & Practical Features - Remote keyless entry, power windows and power door locks for everyday convenience - Cruise control for more relaxed highway driving - Rear cargo area with generous headroom and flexibility for hauling gear, groceries or luggage - Durable interior finishes designed to stand up to daily use The 2018 Kia Soul + delivers an efficient, well-equipped package with a roomy interior and modern connectivity features, all wrapped in a signature black exterior. For detailed equipment verification, available factory options, or to arrange a test drive, please get in touch and we’ll provide complete vehicle specifics.

Why Choose This Kia Soul?
Recent Arrival: Fresh on the lot and ready for its next home.

Pristine Condition: With miles this low and a single-owner history, this vehicle won't stay on the lot for long.

Dont miss out on this incredible value! Experience the unique style and smooth handling of the Kia Soul for yourself.

Call or Text Peterson BMW of Boise today at 208-378-5980 to schedule your test drive!

description:
Introducing the 2017 Subaru Outback 2.5i Premium - the ultimate combination of style, performance, and versatility. This stunning vehicle boasts a spacious interior, advanced technology, and impressive safety features, making it the perfect choice for any adventure.

Step inside and experience the luxurious comfort of the Outback's premium cloth seats, offering ample space for you and your passengers. The dual-zone automatic climate control ensures everyone stays comfortable, no matter the weather outside.

Under the hood, the Outback is powered by a 2.5-liter 4-cylinder engine, delivering a smooth and efficient ride. With Subaru's renowned Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive, you can confidently take on any road condition, from snow-covered streets to muddy trails.

But the Outback isn't just about performance - it's also packed with cutting-edge technology. The 7-inch touchscreen display allows you to access your favorite apps, music, and navigation with ease. And with features such as Bluetooth connectivity and Apple CarPlay/Android Auto compatibility, staying connected on the go has never been easier.

When it comes to safety, the Outback sets the standard. Equipped with Subaru's EyeSight Driver Assist Technology, you'll have peace of mind knowing that your vehicle is actively working to prevent accidents. Features like adaptive cruise control, lane keep assist, and pre-collision braking make every drive safer.

Don't miss your chance to own this 2017 Subaru Outback 2.5i Premium. With its impressive features and spacious design, it's the perfect vehicle for any lifestyle. Hurry in today and experience the Outback for yourself!

description: The 2017 Kia Soul is a fun and lively ride that captures the essence of style and practicality. Its 1.6L GDI DOHC Dual CVVT I4 engine delivers a spirited 130 horsepower, making your daily drives enjoyable and responsive. This front-wheel-drive vehicle combines efficiency and power. It offers impressive fuel economy with 24-25 MPG in the city and up to 30 MPG on the highway, perfect for both short trips and long road adventures. With its sleek Clear White exterior paint, this Soul stands out where it belongs-on the open road. Inside, you'll find comfortable black cloth seats that provide a welcoming atmosphere for all passengers, complemented by features like keyless entry and Bluetooth connectivity for ultimate convenience. The spacious interior allows for versatility with a rear bench seat that easily accommodates passengers or cargo. Additional technology features, including satellite radio and steering wheel audio controls, keep you connected and entertained on every journey. This model also includes essential safety features such as multiple airbags, ABS brakes, stability control, and traction control, ensuring peace of mind while driving. Enjoy the ease of A/C and cruise control as you navigate through your day. The Kia Soul's combination of style, comfort, fuel efficiency, and advanced technology makes it an exceptional choice for anyone looking to enhance their driving experience. With its sporty performance capabilities from the 6-speed automatic transmission with Sportmatic mode, every drive feels lively and engaging.

description:
The 2016 MINI Clubman Cooper S represents a major evolution in the Clubman lineup, transforming the model into a larger, more practical, and more sophisticated compact wagon while still retaining MINI s signature charm, bold styling, and lively handling. Redesigned for the 2016 model year, this generation introduces four full-size doors and a more spacious cabin, making it far more versatile than the quirky three-door predecessor. ?? Engine & PerformanceThe Cooper S version offers a lively and responsive powertrain:
  • Engine: 2.0-liter turbocharged 4-cylinder
  • Horsepower: 189 hp @ 5000 rpm
  • Torque: 207 lb-ft
  • 0 60 mph: approx. 7.0 seconds
  • Drivetrain: Front-wheel drive
  • Transmission options: 6-speed manual or automatic (depending on configuration)
The Cooper S delivers brisk acceleration with strong mid-range torque thanks to its turbocharged engine. Handling remains true to MINI s athletic character sharp steering, taut suspension tuning, and playful cornering, making it fun to drive on city streets and twisty backroads. ? Fuel EfficiencyThe Clubman Cooper S offers respectable efficiency for a sporty compact:
  • EPA fuel economy: 24 MPG city/34 MPG highway/27 MPG combined
This efficiency makes it a practical choice for daily commuting or long-distance travel.?? Dimensions & PracticalityThe 2016 redesign brings a significant increase in size:
  • Length: 167.44 in
  • Width: 70.87 in
  • Height: 56.73 in
Cargo and passenger space are dramatically improved:
  • Cargo capacity:
    • 12.7 cu.ft. behind rear seats
    • Up to 44.1 cu.ft. with seats folded
  • Rear doors: Swing-out barn-style cargo doors
  • Passenger room: Spacious enough for four adults to ride comfortably, with improved legroom and easier entry thanks to four conventional doors.
This makes the Clubman one of the most practical MINI models available.??? Interior & ComfortThe cabin blends retro-modern MINI design with high-quality materials:
  • Circular center display with available infotainment upgrades
  • High-quality textures and customizable ambient lighting
  • Supportive front sport seats
  • Increased rear legroom versus previous generations
  • Optional features include:
    • Harman/Kardon premium audio
    • Panoramic moonroof
    • Navigation
    • Leather upholstery
    • Heated seats
MINI s trademark design cues toggle switches, contrast trim, and unique dashboard elements give the Clubman a distinct character not found in typical compact hatchbacks.?? Technology & FeaturesStandard and available technology includes:
  • Bluetooth connectivity
  • AM/FM audio system
  • Optional rear-view camera, parking sensors, and navigation
  • Multiple customization packages (Tech, Premium, Lighting)
The car features MINI s intuitive infotainment interface (shared with BMW systems), offering modern connectivity and multimedia options.??? Safety & Driver AssistanceThe 2016 Clubman offers several useful safety features:
  • Stability and traction control
  • Brake assist and ABS
  • Available rear-view camera
  • Optional parking distance sensors
  • Available run-flat tires (depending on trim and package)
Its larger dimensions and improved chassis contribute to a secure, confidence-inspiring driving experience.?? Exterior DesignKey exterior highlights include:
  • Signature MINI round headlights and hexagonal grille
  • Longer, wider stance giving it a more wagon-like profile
  • Distinctive rear barn-style doors
  • Available 17-inch wheels and sport trims
  • Customizable color combinations and roof/mirror contrasts
Its quirky yet upscale design makes the Clubman stand apart from mainstream compact cars.Professional SummaryThe 2016 MINI Clubman Cooper S Hatchback 4D delivers:
  • A punchy 189-hp turbocharged engine with agile dynamics
  • A spacious, practical cabin with seating for up to five
  • Larger dimensions than previous Clubman models for improved comfort
  • A premium, customizable interior with signature MINI flair
  • Versatile cargo space with swing-out rear doors
  • Modern infotainment and safety technologies
The 2016 Clubman Cooper S strikes an excellent balance between fun-to-drive personality, everyday usability, and distinctive design, making it an appealing option for drivers seeking something more stylish and engaging than the typical compact hatchback.StartCar prices. We combine data from the local market with this car's mileage, features, and inspection findings to arrive at the most competitive price possible for this vehicle. Taxes, tag, title, registration fees, government fees and dealer service fee of $995 are additional and not included in vehicle prices. These charges represent costs and profit to the dealer for items such as inspecting, cleaning, and adjusting vehicles, and preparing documents related to the sale. While great effort is made to ensure the accuracy of the information on this site, errors do occur so please verify information with a customer service representative. This is easily done by calling us at 305-410-1111 or by visiting us at the dealership.

description:
Experience the ultimate in versatility and safety with this exceptional 2016 Subaru Outback 2.5i Premium. Boasting a sleek white exterior and a meticulously maintained interior, this Outback is the perfect companion for your family's adventures.

Highlighted features include:
• Backup Camera
• Blindspot Monitor
• EyeSight & Blind Spot & Rear Cross Traffic & PRG
• Adaptive Cruise Control
• Steering Responsive Fog Lights (SRF)
• Power Rr Gate w/Automatic Close & Height Memory

The Outback's 2.5L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine, paired with a CVT Lineartronic transmission and Subaru's renowned All-Wheel Drive system, delivers an exceptional driving experience. With an impressive 25 MPG in the city and 33 MPG on the highway, this Outback offers the perfect balance of power and efficiency.

Designed with your safety in mind, this Outback is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including Blind Spot Detection, Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, and the EyeSight system, which provides lane departure and pre-collision warnings to help keep you and your loved ones secure on the road.

The spacious interior of the Outback offers ample room for your family and all their gear, with a split-folding rear seat and generous cargo space. Heated front seats and dual-zone automatic climate control ensure everyone travels in comfort, while the Subaru STARLINK 7.0" Multimedia Plus system keeps you connected and entertained.

Backed by Subaru's reputation for reliability and durability, this 2016 Outback 2.5i Premium is a true standout in the midsize SUV segment. With its exceptional capabilities, advanced safety features, and premium amenities, it's the perfect choice for the discerning buyer who demands the best. Visit our showroom today to experience the Outback for yourself and discover why it's the ideal vehicle for your next adventure.

Designed with the modern work van in mind, the 2023 Ford Transit-250 Base offers a winning combination of power, functionality, and technology. With its array of thoughtful features and proven reliability, this van is the ideal choice for small businesses, tradespeople, and anyone who demands exceptional utility from their work vehicle.

Experience the difference for yourself. Schedule a test drive today and discover how the 2023 Ford Transit-250 Base can transform the way you work.

1-Owner Vehicle

This 2025 Ford Transit‑250 Base is the dependable, high‑capacity cargo van engineered for businesses that need strength, space, and unwavering reliability. With only 11,033 miles, this Transit is barely broken in and ready to handle daily operations with confidence. Whether you’re transporting equipment, making deliveries, or building out a custom work van, the Transit‑250 gives you the capability and flexibility you need.

🚐 Exterior & Interior Design

Body Style: 3D Cargo Van
Exterior Color: Oxford White — clean, sharp, and ideal for business branding
Interior Color: Ebony — durable, functional, and easy to maintain

The Transit‑250 offers a commanding presence on the road, with a tall roofline and wide-opening access points that make loading and unloading simple and efficient.

⚙️ Performance & Capability

Engine: 3.5L V6 Flex Fuel
Drivetrain: RWD (Rear‑Wheel Drive)
Transmission: 10‑Speed Automatic with Overdrive

This Flex Fuel V6 engine provides strong, reliable power for hauling cargo or equipment, while the 10‑speed automatic transmission ensures smooth performance and improved efficiency. RWD gives you solid stability and durability — perfect for commercial use and heavy loads.

📦 Utility & Cargo Functionality
The Transit‑250 Base is designed for work:

Massive cargo space with flat, configurable load area
Perfect for shelving, racks, upfits, or custom builds
Wide sliding side door for easy access
Large rear doors with excellent loading clearance

From contractors to delivery services, this van adapts to your business needs.

📱 Technology & Convenience
Even in its Base trim, the 2025 Transit offers modern features to keep you productive:

Infotainment with Bluetooth® connectivity
Backup camera for safer maneuvering
Steering‑wheel controls for convenience
Multiple storage compartments for tools and paperwork

Everything is built with the working driver in mind.

🛡️ Safety & Ford Engineering
Ford is known for strong safety and durability:

Rear‑view camera
Stability and traction control
Advanced braking systems
High‑strength body design for commercial use

This is a van that delivers safety and confidence on every job.

The 2025 Ford Transit‑250 Base — Your Business. Your Capability. Your Advantage.
If you need a cargo van that offers space, strength, efficiency, and dependability, this 2025 Transit‑250 is ready to get to work today. Clean, capable, and engineered for productivity — it’s the perfect business partner.
If you want a more aggressive sales version, a short social‑media version, or a fleet‑focused version, I can create that too.

This 2025 RAM 2500 ProMaster Cargo Van with a 159" wheelbase and High Roof is the ultimate workhorse designed for maximum productivity and utility. Finished in Bright White Clear-Coat with a durable Black interior featuring vinyl bucket seats, this van is powered by the reliable 3.6L V6 24V VVT Engine and a smooth 9-speed automatic transmission. As showcased on the original window sticker, this ProMaster is equipped with the Tradesman Package 22B and the Convenience Group, adding essential features like power-folding heated mirrors, adaptive cruise control with stop and go, and front fog lamps. The spacious cargo area is enhanced by 260-degree opening rear hinged doors and upper/lower side-wall paneling by Mopar, while the cabin stays connected with a 7-inch Uconnect 5 touchscreen featuring Apple CarPlay and Google Android Auto. description: 2025 RAM ProMaster Tradesman 2500 — White exterior / Gray interior This 2025 RAM ProMaster Tradesman 2500 is finished in a clean white exterior with a gray interior and is in excellent overall condition. It is powered by the Pentastar 3.6L V6 producing 276 hp and 250 lb-ft of torque. The engine is mated to an automatic transmission and the ProMaster’s front-wheel-drive layout helps provide a low load floor and predictable handling when the vehicle is loaded. This unit has a clean CARFAX and a one-owner history. Factory standard features and equipment (commercial/work-focused specification): - Powertrain and chassis - Pentastar 3.6L V6 engine (276 hp / 250 lb-ft) - Automatic transmission paired to the front-wheel-drive chassis for enhanced cargo floor height and maneuverability - Commercial-grade suspension and braking tuned for heavy use and payloads - Steel wheels with durable all-season tires - Cargo and utility - Large, open cargo area designed for easy upfitting and secure storage - Wide rear cargo doors that open to provide unobstructed access for loading - At least one sliding side cargo door for convenient curbside loading and unloading - Factory-installed cargo tie-down points and recessed floor mounting locations to secure loads - Durable, easy-to-clean cargo flooring and panels designed for worksite use - Provisioning for partition or bulkhead installation - Exterior and visibility - Solid white factory paint with black trim accents for a utilitarian, easy-to-maintain finish - Large side mirrors to support improved rearward visibility when hauling cargo - High-mounted brake light and practical exterior lighting for work and road safety - Interior and driver convenience - Gray, commercial-grade seating and trim designed for durability and frequent use - Practical storage: overhead and in-cab storage bins, cupholders and door pockets - Analog instrument cluster with a driver information display providing essential vehicle data - Heating and ventilation with straightforward controls built for reliability - Multiple 12-volt power outlets and at least one USB port for mobile devices and accessories - Infotainment and connectivity - Factory infotainment system with AM/FM radio, Bluetooth hands-free calling and audio streaming, and USB connectivity for device charging and media - Steering wheel controls for basic audio and phone functions - Safety and security - Standard safety systems including anti-lock brakes (ABS), electronic stability control and traction control - Multiple airbags for driver and front passenger - Rearview camera to assist with low-speed maneuvering and loading - Factory door locks and security features appropriate to commercial use This Tradesman 2500 is configured for dependable day-to-day work with the core, factory-installed features you expect in a rugged cargo van: a strong V6 powertrain, practical interior materials, ample cargo access and basic connectivity. The vehicle’s excellent condition, clean CARFAX and single-owner history make it a solid choice for businesses or contractors seeking a ready-to-work commercial van. 2022 Toyota 4Runner Limited 4WD Proven Reliability with Premium Comfort

Intro
This 2022 Toyota 4Runner Limited delivers legendary Toyota durability paired with upscale features and true 4WD capability. A one-owner, well-maintained SUV with a strong service history, its built for long-term ownership and Northwest adventures.

Performance and Capability

4.0L V6 engine producing 270 horsepower and 278 lb-ft of torque

Full-time 4WD with locking center differential and A-TRAC

5-speed automatic transmission with smooth, proven operation

X-REAS Sport Enhancement Suspension for confident on-road handling

Tow hitch receiver with 7- and 4-pin connectors

Hill Start Assist and Downhill Assist Control

Comfort and Technology

Leather-trimmed seating with heated and ventilated front seats

Power tilt-and-slide moonroof

Dual-zone automatic climate control

Premium JBL audio system with navigation

Apple CarPlay and Android Auto compatibility

Power sliding rear window and smart key with push-button start

Safety and Driver Assistance

Toyota Safety Sense P with Pre-Collision System and Pedestrian Detection

Dynamic Radar Cruise Control

Lane Departure Alert and Automatic High Beams

Blind Spot Monitor with Rear Cross-Traffic Alert

Front and rear parking sonar with panoramic view monitor

Warranty

Powertrain warranty remaining: approximately 11 months or 8,863 miles

Corrosion perforation warranty remaining: approximately 11 months

Safety belt and restraint coverage remaining: approximately 11 months or 8,863 miles

Recent Maintenance

Oil and filter changed

Tires rotated and balanced

Rear brake pads replaced and rotors resurfaced

Brake fluid flushed

Regular manufacturer-recommended oil changes documented

Ownership and Condition

CARFAX 1-owner personal vehicle

No accidents or damage reported

Approximately 51,000 miles

Clean title with extensive dealer-documented service history

Well-maintained and ready for immediate use

Buyer Q&A (SEO/AI Block)

Is the 2022 Toyota 4Runner Limited good for off-road use?
Yes. Its full-time 4WD system, locking center differential, and proven V6 make it highly capable on and off pavement.

How reliable is the Toyota 4Runner?
The 4Runner is known for long-term reliability, and this one-owner example has a strong maintenance history.

Does this 4Runner have luxury features?
Yes. The Limited trim includes leather seating, premium JBL audio, navigation, and advanced safety technology.

Is this SUV available locally in Kitsap County?
Yes. This 4Runner is available now at Port Orchard Ford, serving Port Orchard, Bremerton, Silverdale, Gig Harbor, and surrounding areas.

The spacious cargo area offers ample room to transport your essential equipment and supplies, while the thoughtful interior features like the swing-out storage bin and premium cloth seating ensure your crew stays comfortable on the job. Reliability is key in the world of commercial vehicles, and the Chevrolet Express 2500 delivers. Backed by a reputation for rugged dependability, this van is built to withstand the demands of your business. Whether you're hauling heavy loads or navigating tight urban spaces, the Express 2500 has the capabilities to get the job done right.

At our dealership, we understand the importance of finding the perfect work vehicle to support your operations. That's why we're proud to offer this well-equipped 2024 Chevrolet Express 2500 Work Van Cargo. With its impressive features, reliable performance, and versatile design, this van is poised to become an invaluable asset to your business.

We invite you to experience the Chevrolet Express 2500 for yourself. Schedule a test drive today and discover how this capable work van can transform the way you do business. Our knowledgeable sales team is ready to answer any questions you may have and guide you through the purchasing process. Let us help you find the perfect solution to keep your company moving forward.

Vehicle Details
Ready to tackle your toughest jobs — this 2020 Ram ProMaster 2500 High Roof 159WB delivers professional-grade capability with everyday comfort. Located in Murfreesboro, TN, this certified pre-owned van pairs a durable V6 3.6L gasoline/E85 engine with efficient FWD handling to give you confident performance and excellent cargo capacity in a maneuverable package.

This ProMaster is priced to move — the best price around — making it an unbeatable value for contractors, delivery services, or anyone needing a reliable work van. The high roof and 159-inch wheelbase provide generous cargo volume and flexible upfit potential, while the certified pre-owned status and CARFAX 1-Owner history give you added peace of mind.

Stay connected and secure on the road with modern conveniences including Hands-Free Bluetooth for safe calling and media, a Back-Up Camera for precise reversing, and Rear Parking Sensors to help prevent dents and dings in tight spaces. Ergonomic driver-focused controls and durable interior surfaces make long shifts easier, and the powerful 3.6L V6 engine offers the torque you need for loaded runs.

If you want top utility, verified history, and the best price in Murfreesboro, TN, this 2020 Ram ProMaster 2500 High Roof is ready to work. Contact us to schedule a test drive and see why this certified pre-owned van is the smartest choice for your business or fleet.

Equipment
The high efficiency automatic transmission shifts smoothly and allows you to relax while driving. Set the temperature exactly where you are most comfortable in the vehicle. The fan speed and temperature will automatically adjust to maintain your preferred zone climate. Easily set your speed in this unit with a state of the art cruise control system. Increase or decrease velocity with the touch of a button. Quickly unlock the vehicle with keyless entry. The vehicle features a hands-free Bluetooth phone system.

With a robust 2.5L 4-cylinder engine generating 182 horsepower, this Forester Sport is designed to deliver a reliable and efficient performance.Safety is a top priority with standard features such as ABS, electronic stability control (ESC), and a full array of airbags including front, side, knee, and curtain airbags for enhanced protection. The vehicle comes equipped with advanced driver assistance systems like forward collision warning, lane departure warning, and pedestrian automatic emergency braking, ensuring a secure driving experience.Featuring all-wheel drive (AWD) for superior handling in various road conditions, this Subaru Forester Sport is equipped with a continuously variable transmission (CVT) for seamless acceleration. The lower beam headlamps utilize LED technology for improved visibility, while the semiautomatic headlamp beam switching adds convenience during night-time drives.Inside, the Forester Sport offers seating for up to five occupants with front seat-mounted side airbags and roof-mounted side curtain airbags for additional safety. Enjoy the convenience of manual seat belts, direct tire pressure monitoring system (TPMS), and a rear visibility system for enhanced awareness while reversing.Additional features include a sporty design with a wagon body style, a wheelbase suitable for urban and outdoor adventures, and a total curb weight tailored for efficiency and agility. Complementing its practical side, this Subaru model offers modern amenities like keyless ignition, a high-end Harman Kardon entertainment system, smart entry and push-start functionality, and built-in navigation for seamless travels.For anyone seeking a versatile crossover that combines style, safety, and performance, the 2024 Subaru Forester Sport stands out as an exceptional choice, now available for a test drive at Schomp Hyundai.

Finished in Diamond Black Crystal Pearl-Coat over a stylish Global Black interior, this Grand Cherokee stands tall with the upgraded Black Appearance Package, which includes:

20-inch Gloss Black Aluminum Wheels

265/50R20 performance all-season tires

Gloss Black exterior accents

10.1” Uconnect® 5 NAV touchscreen

Apple CarPlay® & Android Auto™

Heated leather-wrapped steering wheel

Capri leatherette seating surfaces

Safety is also a major highlight:

Adaptive Cruise Control with Stop & Go

Blind Spot Monitoring + Rear Cross-Path Detection

ParkSense® Rear Park Assist with Stop

Forward Collision Warning Plus

Active Lane Management + Auto High Beams

Rear-Seat Object Alert

This Grand Cherokee received its most recent oil and filter service in May 2025, with prior inspections and nitrogen tire fill documented by Jeep. With its 5yr/60K powertrain warranty and 3yr/36K basic warranty still active, it’s ready for years of dependable adventure.

Whether you’re commuting in style or heading off the beaten path, this Grand Cherokee Limited 4x4 blends luxury, tech, and capability into one stunning SUV. Don’t wait — this low-mileage, high-style Jeep won’t last. 🖤🛻🌟

Porsche Oklahoma City is proud to present this 2023 Porsche Cayenne Turbo Coupe, a commanding performance SUV that blends unmistakable Turbo power with coupe-inspired design and everyday refinement. Finished in Carrara White Metallic over a Black Leather Interior, this one-owner example has been meticulously maintained and comes backed by a Porsche Certified Pre-Owned 2-year/unlimited mileage warranty, along with a clean CARFAX report for added peace of mind.

With its Turbo designation, this Cayenne Coupe delivers exhilarating acceleration, confident handling, and an elevated driving experience—while still offering the comfort, technology, and versatility expected of a Porsche luxury SUV. A thoughtfully selected set of driver-assistance and premium comfort features make this Turbo Coupe equally impressive on long journeys or spirited drives.

Highlights & Premium Equipment

```html
2012 Ford E350 Super Duty Passenger XLT Extended Van for Sale in Fontana, CA
Discover the Perfect Passenger Van at Divine Auto Mall
Looking for a spacious, reliable, and versatile passenger van? The 2012 Ford E350 Super Duty Passenger XLT Extended Van is now available at Divine Auto Mall, conveniently located in Fontana, San Bernardino, California. Whether you need a vehicle for family outings, business transportation, or group travel, this van is designed to meet your needs with comfort and efficiency.
Powerful Performance: V8, 5.4-Liter Engine
The 2012 Ford E350 Super Duty Passenger XLT Extended Van is powered by a robust V8, 5.4-liter engine. This powerhouse delivers the performance and reliability you need to tackle long drives or heavy passenger loads. With its automatic 4-speed transmission with overdrive, this van ensures smooth and efficient gear shifts, making it a joy to drive whether you're navigating city streets or hitting the open highway.
Spacious 11-Passenger Seating
Need to transport a crowd? The 2012 Ford E350 Super Duty Passenger XLT Extended Van offers 11-passenger seating, making it ideal for large families, shuttle services, or group travel. The extended design ensures ample legroom and headroom for everyone on board, making long journeys comfortable and enjoyable. If you're looking for a vehicle that prioritizes space and convenience, this van has you covered.
Comfort Features for Everyone
Comfort is key in the 2012 Ford E350 Super Duty Passenger XLT Extended Van. This van is equipped with dual-zone air conditioning to keep the driver and passengers cool, even on the hottest California days. The rear air conditioning ensures that passengers in the back stay just as comfortable as those in the front. Whether you're heading to the beach or taking a road trip through San Bernardino, everyone will enjoy the ride.
Advanced Entertainment and Connectivity
Stay connected and entertained on the go with the 2012 Ford E350 Super Duty Passenger XLT Extended Van. This vehicle comes equipped with a CD/MP3 player and AM/FM stereo, so you can enjoy your favorite music, podcasts, or radio stations. Additionally, the Ford SYNC system and Sirius Satellite radio enhance your driving experience by providing seamless connectivity and a wide range of entertainment options.
Safety and Stability Features You Can Trust
Safety is a top priority in the 2012 Ford E350 Super Duty Passenger XLT Extended Van. This van is equipped with Traction Control and AdvanceTrac technology to help maintain stability and control in various driving conditions. The ABS (4-Wheel) braking system ensures reliable stopping power, while dual airbags provide added protection for the driver and front passenger. Whether you're navigating busy streets or cruising on the highway, you can drive with confidence.
Convenience and Practicality
The 2012 Ford E350 Super Duty Passenger XLT Extended Van is designed with convenience in mind. Features like power door locks, power windows, and power steering make daily driving and operation effortless. The cruise control feature allows for a more relaxed driving experience on long trips, while the tilt steering wheel ensures a comfortable driving position for drivers of all sizes.
Durable and Stylish Exterior
The 2012 Ford E350 Super Duty Passenger XLT Extended Van boasts a durable and stylish exterior that is built to last. Its rugged design is complemented by steel wheels, which not only enhance the van's appearance but also provide long-lasting durability. Whether you're using this van for personal or commercial purposes, its solid construction will stand up to the demands of daily use.
Handling Package for a Smooth Ride
The Handling Package included with the 2012 Ford E350 Super Duty Passenger XLT Extended Van ensures a smooth and comfortable ride, even when the van is fully loaded. This feature enhances the vehicle's stability and performance, making it easier to handle on winding roads or uneven terrain. Whether you're driving through the streets of Fontana or exploring the scenic routes of San Bernardino, this van delivers a confident and enjoyable driving experience.
Why Choose the 2012 Ford E350 Super Duty Passenger XLT Extended Van?
The 2012 Ford E350 Super Duty Passenger XLT Extended Van is the ultimate solution for anyone in need of a spacious and reliable vehicle. Its combination of power, comfort, and practicality makes it a standout choice for families, businesses, and organizations. With its impressive features and versatile design, this van is ready to meet your transportation needs.
Visit Divine Auto Mall in Fontana, CA Today
Ready to see the 2012 Ford E350 Super Duty Passenger XLT Extended Van for yourself? Visit Divine Auto Mall in Fontana, San Bernardino, California, today. Our friendly and knowledgeable team is here to help you find the perfect vehicle for your needs. Don't miss out on this incredible passenger van—stop by our dealership and take it for a test drive!
For more information about the 2012 Ford E350 Super Duty Passenger XLT Extended Van, contact Divine Auto Mall in Fontana, CA. We look forward to helping you find your next vehicle!
```

description: Welcome to Dave Mungenast St. Louis Honda. We are one of the St. Louis area's largest Honda dealers. Founded in 1965 the Mungenast family has served the St. Louis area with its automotive needs for 60 years. As the #1 volume Honda dealership in Missouri for 33 consecutive years, a 18-time president's award winner, a Honda Master Circle Award Winner, and a 4-time BBB Torch award winner, we are proud to serve the community with honest and transparent business practices. Experience luxury, power, and advanced safety in this Black 2022 Honda Pilot AWD Black Edition. Powered by a robust 3.5L V6 engine and paired with a 9-speed shiftable automatic transmission, this SUV delivers confident performance and all-weather capability with on-demand AWD. Enjoy premium features like leather-trimmed upholstery, heated and ventilated front seats, a panoramic moonroof, and a power-operated rear liftgate. Stay connected and entertained with an 8-inch touchscreen, Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, wireless charging, and a rear Blu-Ray/DVD entertainment system. Safety is paramount with adaptive cruise control, lane keeping assist, blind spot monitoring, rear cross traffic alert, and Honda Sensing driver-assist technologies. The spacious interior seats up to eight, with flat-folding third-row seats and up to 15 cupholders, making it perfect for families or road trips. Remote engine start, rain-sensing wipers, and premium audio further enhance comfort and convenience. Stand out with exclusive Black Edition details, including blacked-out trim, wheels, and roof rails. Discover the ideal blend of style, technology, and versatility in this well-equipped Honda Pilot. 2022 ALG Residual Value Award: Mass Market Brand, 2022 Kelley Blue Book Best Family Cars, 2022 Kelley Blue Book Brand Image Awards: Best Overall Brand

The GT3 s naturally aspirated flat-six is one of the last of its kind razor-sharp throttle response, spine-tingling acoustics, and a crescendo to 9,000 RPM that feels mechanical, analog, and alive.Premium Features

This GT3 s configuration, PCCB, carbon roof, full buckets, and Neodyme wheels, places it firmly in the upper tier of enthusiast-spec builds. The 9,000-RPM naturally aspirated flat-six, paired with lightning-fast PDK shifts and a motorsport-derived chassis, creates a level of connection few modern cars can replicate. Steering feel, balance, and response are engineered with surgical precision this is a road-legal race car built with intent.Contact Loren AutoPremium vehicles, genuine relationships, and an experience that feels like family.

Safety and Security
  • The vehicle is equipped with a system that senses, and then prepares, the vehicle and/or occupants, for an impending forward collision.
  • The vehicle constantly monitors the roadway in front of the vehicle and identifies and tracks pedestrians on an interior display. If the system determines a likely impact, it will automatically take preventative steps to avoid hitting the pedestrian.
  • The vehicle is equipped with a camera that displays an image of the area behind the vehicle on an interior display.
  • An active lane departure system alerts the driver of unintended movement of the vehicle out of a designated traffic lane and automatically maintains the vehicle's position within that lane.
Technology and Telematics
  • Mobile devices can wirelessly connect to the internet through the vehicle's private mobile network.

description: Introducing the captivating 2024 Chevrolet Corvette E-Ray 2LZ, a remarkable fusion of cutting-edge technology and uncompromising performance. This stunning sports car, finished in a vibrant Green exterior, is a true testament to Chevrolet's engineering excellence. Prepare to be mesmerized by the array of premium features that elevate the driving experience, including: - Front Lift Adjustable Height with Memory - GT2 Bucket Seats - Convertible Top with Carbon Flash Nacelles and Roof - Jake C8.R Graphics Package - ZER Performance Package - Stealth Interior Trim Package - Orange-Painted Calipers - Sueded Microfiber-Wrapped Steering Wheel Step inside and immerse yourself in the Corvette's cutting-edge technology, with a Bose Performance Series Sound System, Wireless Charging, and a state-of-the-art Infotainment System. The Heads-Up Display and Performance Data Video Recorder further enhance the driver's connection to the road. This 2024 Chevrolet Corvette E-Ray 2LZ has been meticulously inspected and certified, ensuring it meets the highest standards of quality and reliability. With just 1,175 miles on the odometer, this exceptional sports car is practically brand new, offering you the opportunity to own a true automotive masterpiece. Powered by a potent 6.2L V8 engine and equipped with an 8-Speed Dual Clutch transmission, the Corvette E-Ray delivers an exhilarating driving experience, with an impressive fuel efficiency of 16 city and 24 highway MPGe. The advanced ZER Suspension and Magnetic Selective Ride Control provide unparalleled handling and responsiveness, allowing you to conquer the open road with confidence. This Corvette E-Ray 2LZ is a rare find, and we invite you to experience its exceptional performance and cutting-edge features firsthand. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why this sports car is the ultimate expression of Chevrolet's engineering prowess. Prepare to be captivated by the power, style, and innovation that define the 2024 Chevrolet Corvette E-Ray 2LZ.

ABOUT US: Rich's Cars is a family-run dealership that focuses on the customer first. Rich has been in the car business for 25 years and is experienced in providing excellent quality vehicles. You don't last in this business without treating people the right way. We offer a low-pressure buying experience, with salesman that act more like friends than vultures. All of our vehicles undergo thorough multi-point inspections to ensure they are mechanically sound. Have questions about our service? Check out our reviews! Give us a call or send us a text at 435-752-7424!
BRANDED TITLES: We sell rebuilt/restored vehicles because they offer superior value for our clients. All of our branded cars go through very rigorous and thorough testing. We oversee the build process to ensure our standards are met. We will NEVER sell a car that we feel has been structurally compromised or unsafe in any way. This means NO cut corners, NO safety issues. All branded cars go through 3 sets of eyes to ensure the best cars are being sold. A 3 month bumper to bumper warranty free-of-charge is included with the purchase of a rebuilt title. Ask us what was repaired on them! BUY BRANDED to save thousands on your next car -- and get a better bang for your buck. We believe there is NO better value than a Rich's R/R title vehicle.
OUR WARRANTY: ‘Bumper to bumper‘ coverage for 3 months/3,000 miles is offered for all branded titles and cars under 100k miles. This covers any mechanical malfunction with the car following the purchase, with $0 deductible. We guarantee our cars because we trust them. We offer this same warranty coverage for up to 5 years at an additional cost. Our extended warranties are NOT 3rd party warranties, so there is no run-around in getting repairs covered (no 1-800 numbers, paperwork, etc). It is a no-hassle service offered for the convenience of our customers.
FINANCING: With a seasoned team of finance professionals, we have the knowledge and experience to get you the very best rate for your credit experience. Credit Union financing is available. We will never increase the price for outside financing, cash payments, or other arrangements. We offer competitive rates for financing and can regularly get rates lower than what you have been quoted elsewhere. You can apply for financing on our website at: https://www.richscarsncredit.c... (https://www.richscarsncredit.com/financing)
NATIONWIDE SHIPPING: At an additional cost, we can arrange shipping to anywhere in the continental United States. Reach out to us and we can provide an estimate for shipping. We regularly sell cars out of state, due to our service, inventory, and pricing.
NO BIG DEALER BS: $399 DOC FEE is the only dealership fee we have. Utah residents are subject to 7.3% sales tax, and registration fees. We will never raise the price on a car for cash payment or outside financing.
If you have any questions, please reach out to 435-752-7424!
Have questions about our service? Check out our reviews!

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2023 Lexus RX. This meticulously maintained, one-owner vehicle boasts a clean CARFAX history, ensuring you can purchase with confidence.

• CLEAN CARFAX
• ONE OWNER

Powered by a robust 2.4L I4 PDI Turbocharged DOHC 16V engine, this RX delivers an impressive 275 horsepower, paired with an 8-Speed Automatic transmission and All-Wheel Drive for a seamless and responsive driving experience. With an EPA-estimated 21 MPG in the city and 28 MPG on the highway, this Lexus offers exceptional fuel efficiency to complement its dynamic performance.

• Navigation System
• 12 Speakers
• Power Driver Seat
• Power Steering

The RX's well-appointed interior features a wealth of premium amenities, including a Navigation System, 12-Speaker Audio System, Power Driver's Seat, and Power Steering. Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control, a Rear Window Defroster, and a Power Liftgate ensure your comfort and convenience.

For your safety and peace of mind, this Lexus is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including Blind Spot Monitoring, Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, and a Rear-View Camera. Airbags, ABS Brakes, and Electronic Stability Control provide additional layers of protection.

With its sleek, modern styling and exceptional build quality, this 2023 Lexus RX is a true testament to the brand's commitment to excellence. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by this exceptional vehicle.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this stunning 2021 Jeep Grand Cherokee L Overland. This exceptional SUV is a true testament to Jeep's commitment to exceptional craftsmanship and uncompromising performance.

Highlighted features include:
• Luxury Tech Group IV
• Uconnect 5 NAV with 10.1" Display
• Trailer Tow Group (B)

This Grand Cherokee L Overland is equipped with a powerful 3.6L V6 engine, delivering an impressive balance of power and efficiency. With 19 city/26 highway MPG, you'll enjoy the perfect blend of capability and fuel economy.

The exterior of this Jeep exudes confidence and sophistication, with a stunning White paint color that commands attention. The 20" machined face aluminum wheels and sleek design elements further enhance the vehicle's premium aesthetic.

Step inside and you'll be greeted by a cabin that redefines luxury. The Nappa leather-trimmed seats, heated and ventilated for your comfort, provide a truly indulgent driving experience. The Luxury Tech Group IV adds a host of advanced features, including 4-zone automatic temperature control, front passenger power seat back massage, and a wireless charging pad for your devices.

The Uconnect 5 NAV system with a 10.1" touchscreen display puts a world of connectivity and entertainment at your fingertips. Enjoy the premium 19-speaker McIntosh audio system, seamless smartphone integration, and turn-by-turn navigation to guide you on your adventures.

Whether you're embarking on a family road trip or tackling the demands of your daily commute, this 2021 Jeep Grand Cherokee L Overland is the perfect companion. Experience the perfect blend of capability, comfort, and technology that will elevate your driving experience.

This vehicle has a notation on the Carfax that it was reacquired by the manufacturer. Simply put, the customer had a complaint about the vehicle and asked the manufacturer to take the car back. As a result, the trade value or selling price you will get for this vehicle is likely to be lower than for a similar vehicle that was not reacquired. This is reflected in the price you are paying for the vehicle now and why the vehicle is less expensive than a similar one that was not reacquired. In time, the difference in value between this vehicle and a normal vehicle will shrink. Therefore, if you plan to keep the vehicle for an extended period of time you will likely capture more of the savings of the lower price than if you sell or trade the vehicle within a short period after purchasing it. description: Prepare for adventure with this versatile 2021 Ford Ranger Crew Cab 4WD, finished in a crisp Oxford White. This mid-size pickup is the perfect partner for both the job site and the trail, powered by a punchy 2.3L EcoBoost engine that delivers a best-in-class 310 lb-ft of torque. Whether you're navigating city streets or exploring the backroads of Arkansas, you'll have the power and agility you need, paired with a smooth 10-speed automatic transmission for effortless driving.This Ranger is uniquely equipped with both the Black Appearance Package and the Sport Appearance Package, giving it a bold, modern look. You'll stand out with 18-inch black-painted wheels, a black grille with a magnetic surround, and black running boards. The Tough Bed Spray-In Bedliner ensures your truck bed stays protected from scratches and dents, while the Class IV Trailer Hitch Receiver means you're always ready to hook up the boat or trailer for a weekend getaway.For those who crave the dirt, the FX4 Off-Road Package turns this Ranger into a true trail machine. It features an Off-Road Tuned Suspension, skid plates to protect vital components, and an Electronic-Locking Rear Differential for maximum traction in tough spots. Combined with the Terrain Management System, you can easily adjust the truck's performance to handle mud, sand, or snow with total confidence.Inside, the cabin is packed with technology to make every trip more enjoyable. The Technology Package adds Adaptive Cruise Control and Navigation, while Apple CarPlay and Android Auto keep your favorite apps right at your fingertips. Comfort is a priority with Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control and a leather-wrapped steering wheel. Plus, with a CARFAX One-Owner and Clean CARFAX history, you can drive away knowing this truck has been exceptionally well-maintained.Allow us to show you how easy it is to do business with the Superior Pre-Owned Superstore of Bentonville. We have quality used Cars, Trucks, and SUVs, and we are ready to help you find out exactly what your trade is worth! Our vehicles have been professionally cleaned and serviced to ensure you drive off the lot feeling like you've purchased a brand-new car. Its what you deserve. Visit http://www.bentonvillepreowned.com or call today!Faster. Simpler. More Transparent. Superior Automotive Group has helped thousands of customers find the right car by leveraging one of Arkansas' largest selections of new and pre-owned vehicles at unparalleled prices. Yet, it's our extra-mile customer service and uncommonly candid and respectful staff that have won the trust and loyalty of Arkansas drivers for 30 years. Come visit one of our Superior dealerships today and let us exceed your expectations.
