description:
Discover the perfect blend of capability, style, and technology in this stunning 2022 Subaru Crosstrek Limited. With its sleek yellow exterior and impressive 2.5L 4-cylinder DOHC 16V engine paired with Lineartronic CVT and Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive, this Crosstrek is ready to take on any adventure.

Highlighted features include:
• Moonroof Package 1
• Exterior & Interior Auto-Dimming Mirrors

This Crosstrek Limited is equipped with a host of premium amenities to elevate your driving experience. Enjoy the convenience of the Subaru STARLINK 8.0" Multimedia Plus System, complete with smartphone integration, as well as the comfort of heated front seats and a power driver's seat. The dual-zone automatic climate control and rear window defroster will keep you and your passengers cozy, no matter the weather.

Safety is a top priority in this Crosstrek, with features like Subaru's advanced EyeSight Driver Assist Technology, Blind Spot Detection with Lane Change Assist, and Rear Cross-Traffic Alert. You can drive with confidence, knowing you and your loved ones are well-protected.

Beyond its impressive capabilities, this Crosstrek Limited boasts a stylish and sophisticated exterior. The 18-inch alloy wheels, body-color bumpers, and power moonroof create a striking presence on the road. The interior is equally impressive, with a leather-trimmed cabin and premium touches throughout.

With an EPA-estimated 27 city/34 highway MPG, this Crosstrek Limited offers exceptional fuel efficiency, making it an ideal choice for your daily commute or weekend adventures. And with just 75,854 miles on the odometer, this Crosstrek is ready to provide many more miles of reliable and enjoyable driving.

Discover the perfect blend of versatility, technology, and style in this 2022 Subaru Crosstrek Limited. Schedule a test drive today and experience the difference for yourself. We're confident you'll be impressed by this exceptional vehicle.

description:
The 2023 Ford F-150 Tremor is an impressive truck that comes with several package options to enhance your driving experience. The highest MSRP package is the Equipment Group 402A High, which boasts an array of premium features including automatic full-time 4WD, heated seats, and advanced safety technologies like Pro Trailer Backup Assist. This package ensures that you have everything you need for a powerful and comfortable ride.

Next, the Bed Utility Package adds practical features such as a power open and close tailgate, integrated tailgate step, and LED in-box lighting, making it perfect for those who frequently utilize their truck bed for work or recreation. The Trailer Tow Package further enhances towing capabilities, equipping the F-150 Tremor with a trailer wiring harness and Pro Trailer Hitch Assist, ensuring that you can tow with confidence.

For tech enthusiasts, the Ford Co-Pilot360 Assist 2.0 package offers cutting-edge safety and navigation features. With adaptive cruise control, lane-keeping alert, and pedestrian impact prevention, this package makes driving safer and more enjoyable. The integrated Wi-Fi hotspot allows you to stay connected on the go, ensuring that your devices are always online.

Under the hood, the F-150 Tremor is powered by a robust EcoBoost 3.5L V-6 engine, delivering a remarkable 400 horsepower paired with a 10-speed automatic transmission. This powerful combination not only provides impressive acceleration but also enhances fuel efficiency, making it a great choice for both daily commutes and weekend adventures.

The 2023 Ford F-150 Tremor is equipped with top features such as the hands-on steering assist system, which maintains your vehicles lane position with minimal input, and the rear collision mitigation system that prepares the vehicle for any potential rear-end accidents. With a rear camera and lane departure prevention system, this truck is designed with safety at the forefront.

In summary, the 2023 Ford F-150 Tremor, with its various packages including the Equipment Group 402A High, Bed Utility Package, Trailer Tow Package, and Ford Co-Pilot360 Assist 2.0, is a versatile and capable truck that meets the needs of any driver. Whether youre looking for power, utility, or advanced technology, the F-150 Tremor has it all.

Elevate Your Driving Experience with the Captivating 2024 Acura Integra Type S

Discover the perfect blend of performance, style, and innovation in the 2024 Acura Integra Type S. This remarkable sports sedan is a true testament to Acura's commitment to crafting vehicles that inspire and excite. With its sleek exterior, powerful engine, and a wealth of premium features, the Integra Type S is poised to redefine your driving experience.

• Protection Film Package
• Heads-Up Display

Immerse yourself in the thrill of the open road with the Integra Type S's impressive 2.0L I4 DOHC 16V engine, mated to a smooth 6-Speed Manual transmission. This dynamic powertrain delivers an exhilarating 21 city/28 highway MPG, ensuring you can conquer the streets with confidence and efficiency.

Elevate your commute and weekend adventures with the Integra Type S's comprehensive suite of advanced technologies. Enjoy the convenience of Apple CarPlay/Android Auto, the clarity of the Navigation system, and the sheer indulgence of the Panoramic Moonroof. The Heads-Up Display keeps your vital information in your line of sight, allowing you to stay focused on the road ahead.

Acura Precision Certified vehicles undergo a rigorous 182-point inspection, ensuring the highest standards of quality and reliability. With a Transferable Warranty, Roadside Assistance, and a $0 Deductible, you can drive with the utmost peace of mind. The Powertrain Limited Warranty extends coverage for up to 84 months/100,000 miles, further solidifying the Integra Type S's long-term value.

Discover the true essence of performance and sophistication in the 2024 Acura Integra Type S. This captivating sports sedan is the embodiment of Acura's unwavering commitment to engineering excellence and customer satisfaction. Experience the thrill for yourself and schedule a test drive today.

Certified as a low-mileage, one-owner vehicle, this 2024 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 LTZ is a true gem. With its impressive capabilities, premium features, and unparalleled safety, it's the perfect choice for those who demand the best in a full-size pickup.

We invite you to experience the power and luxury of this exceptional Silverado. Schedule a test drive today and let us show you why this truck is the ultimate choice for work, play, and everything in between.

description:
Experience the pinnacle of capability, comfort, and style with this 2024 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 High Country. This exceptional full-size pickup is the embodiment of Chevrolet's commitment to engineering excellence, designed to elevate your driving experience to new heights.

• Clean CarFax
• High Country Premium Package
• Adaptive Ride Control Suspension
• Power-Retractable Assist Steps
• Pwr-Adjustable Vertical Trailering Outside Mirrors
• Tri-Fold Soft Tonneau Cover (LPO)
• Wheels: 22" x 9" Painted Aluminum

Boasting a powerful EcoTec3 5.3L V8 engine and a smooth-shifting 10-Speed Automatic transmission, this Silverado 1500 High Country delivers the performance you demand, with an impressive 4WD capability that ensures you're ready to tackle any terrain. The adaptive ride control suspension provides a refined and responsive ride, while the power-retractable assist steps and adjustable trailering mirrors make accessing the cabin and maneuvering with confidence a breeze.

Step inside this remarkable High Country model and discover a world of premium amenities designed to elevate your driving experience. The 12.3" multicolor reconfigurable digital display, Bose premium audio system, and heated and ventilated front seats are just a few of the features that set this Silverado apart. The multi-flex tailgate, power sunroof, and 120-volt power outlets further enhance the versatility and convenience of this exceptional vehicle.

Safety is also a top priority, with a suite of advanced driver assistance technologies, including Adaptive Cruise Control, Lane Keep Assist, and Rear Cross Traffic Braking, ensuring you and your passengers can travel with confidence. The Chevrolet Infotainment 3 Premium system with built-in Wi-Fi hotspot capability and seamless smartphone integration keeps you connected and entertained on the go.

With a sleek black exterior and a well-appointed interior, this 2024 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 High Country is a true head-turner. Its combination of power, capability, and luxury makes it the perfect choice for those who demand the best from their full-size pickup.

Experience the difference for yourself. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate the exceptional features and capabilities of this remarkable Silverado. We're confident you'll be impressed by its uncompromising quality and the value it delivers. Take the next step towards owning the ultimate in truck perfection.

Safety and driver assistance features include a blind spot monitor with lane change assist, an exterior parking camera, and Parking Support Alert with Brake for added confidence in tight spaces. description:
Elevate your off-road adventures with this exceptional 2021 Jeep Gladiator Rubicon. Boasting a commanding presence and unparalleled capability, this rugged pickup is ready to conquer any terrain you dare to explore.

Meticulously equipped, this Gladiator Rubicon features an impressive array of premium features, including:

- 3.0L V6 Diesel Turbocharged engine
- 8-Speed Automatic transmission with Selec-Speed Control
- 8.4" Radio & Premium Audio Group with GPS Navigation
- Advanced Safety Group with Forward Collision Warning Plus
- Cold Weather Group with Heated Steering Wheel and Seats
- LED Lighting Group for enhanced visibility
- Trailer Tow Package for your hauling needs
- Auxiliary Switch Group for added versatility
- Integrated Off-Road Camera for enhanced visibility

The Gladiator Rubicon's exceptional 4x4 performance is further enhanced by its sturdy steel front bumper, body-color fender flares, and Jeep Trail Rated capabilities. Enjoy the open-air freedom of the removable 3-piece hard top, complemented by the convenience of the rear sliding window.

Step inside the spacious cabin and you'll be greeted by premium leather-trimmed bucket seats, a full-length floor console, and a host of advanced technology features. The Uconnect 4C infotainment system with an 8.4" touchscreen display puts navigation, entertainment, and connectivity at your fingertips.

With its impressive off-road prowess, robust construction, and exceptional list of features, this 2021 Jeep Gladiator Rubicon is the ultimate adventure companion. Experience the thrill of the open road and the freedom of the trail like never before. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and discover the true meaning of capability.

Discover the unparalleled power and versatility of the 2023 GMC Sierra 1500 Pro. This exceptional truck is the perfect blend of rugged capability and refined sophistication, designed to elevate your driving experience to new heights.

Boasting an impressive array of features, this Sierra 1500 Pro is the ultimate partner for your adventures. Key highlights include:

• Limited 6-month or 6,000-mile Warranty
• One Owner
• Clean CARFAX
• Convenience Package
• Bed Liner, Spray-On

Under the hood, you'll find a powerful 2.7L I4 Turbocharged DOHC 16V engine that delivers an exhilarating 310 horsepower, seamlessly paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission and rear-wheel drive. This potent powertrain not only provides exceptional performance but also achieves an impressive fuel efficiency of 19 MPG in the city and 22 MPG on the highway, ensuring you can conquer the open road with confidence.

Beyond its impressive capabilities, the Sierra 1500 Pro also boasts a wealth of advanced technology features to enhance your driving experience. Enjoy the convenience of Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, the clarity of the backup camera, and the added safety of features like Blind Spot Monitor, Lane Departure Warning, and Automatic Emergency Braking. The Leather-wrapped steering wheel and heated front seats provide a touch of luxury, while the Keyless Start and Remote Start ensure you're always ready to hit the road.

Whether you're tackling tough terrain, hauling heavy loads, or simply enjoying the open road, the 2023 GMC Sierra 1500 Pro is the ultimate companion. Experience the perfect blend of power, technology, and refinement – schedule a test drive today and discover the difference for yourself.

description:
2023 FERRARI SF90 STRADALE

BLU TOUR DE FRANCE, SUSPENSION LIFTER, CARBON DRIVER ZONE W/LEDS, LOW MILES, AND MORE!

OVERVIEW
The 2023 Ferrari SF90 Stradale is an embodiment of Ferrari mid-engine V8 mastery and a direct descendant of Maranello, Italy's most celebrated performance lineage. As the brand's first production PHEV, the SF90 Stradale combines electrification with traditional Ferrari soul, creating an experience that is technologically advanced yet still emotionally intoxicating. Under the rear glass sits a 4.0-liter twin-turbocharged V8, paired with three electric motors for a combined output of 986 horsepower. Power is sent to all four wheels through an 8-speed dual-clutch transmission, making the SF90 the first Ferrari plug-in hybrid with AWD. The result? A blistering 0-60 mph in just 2.5 seconds and handling precision that pushes the limits of what a road car can do. Rather than a rear spoiler that raises above certain speeds, the SF90 activates its active aero features by dropping a wedge-shaped panel to reveal a Gurney flap spoiler––a fast-acting system that generates as much as 860 pounds of downforce. Behind the wheel, the cabin wraps the driver in Nero/Giallo Leather, with the signature manettino steering wheel and carbon fiber trim reminding you of its performance intentions. The integration of digital displays with classic analog cues ensures a driving experience that is both modern and timeless. Every switch, paddle, and display is positioned toward the driver for maximum engagement, while your plus one gets a Passenger Display to enjoy the thrill.

description: Behold, a one-of-a-kind masterpiece that seamlessly combines classic ruggedness with modern innovation! This ECD built 1995 Land Rover Range Rover County Classic has been transformed into an eco-conscious marvel with a Tesla electric power plant, offering unparalleled performance and sustainability. It's not just a vehicle, it's an experience!****This vehicle has been featured in numerous articles such as Morot Trend, GQ, Carscoops, and Autoblog, and more**** Features:Tesla Electric Conversion: This Range Rover County Classic has been fitted with a state-of-the-art Tesla electric power plant, making it not only eco-friendly but also incredibly powerful and silent.Fully Redone Interior: Step inside to discover a completely refurbished interior. Every inch has been meticulously upgraded with high-quality materials, ensuring comfort and luxury at its finest.Stunning Exterior: The exterior of this beauty has been fully restored, preserving its timeless design while enhancing its overall appearance. It's a head-turner wherever it goes.Immaculate Condition: This vehicle has been cared for with the utmost attention to detail, resulting in an immaculate condition that's ready to impress even the most discerning buyers.Unique and Rare: The combination of a classic Land Rover Range Rover County Classic with a Tesla electric power plant is incredibly rare, making this vehicle a collector's dream.Additional Information:This unique Land Rover Range Rover County Classic offers the best of both worlds: classic styling and the latest in electric vehicle technology. Enjoy the convenience of zero emissions, instant torque, and a quiet, smooth ride while turning heads wherever you go.Contact Information:If you're ready to own this exceptional Land Rover Range Rover County Classic with a Tesla electric power plant conversion, contact us today at Galpin Motors. Don't miss your chance to own a piece of automotive history that's both stunning and eco-friendly. This classic beauty won't last long, so schedule a test drive and experience the future of vintage automobiles!ECD's fully custom builds move through 20 different assembly stations, for a total investment of around 2,200 hours of labor. Tesla-fying a vintage Rover is done in such a way as to preserve as much of the original structure and driving dynamics as possible. So the Tesla motor and direct drive unit are turned 90 degrees and mounted about where the old transfer case went. So instead of powering the left and right rear wheels of a Model S, the Tesla bits power the two offset driveshafts that spin the original live axles with a straight-up 50/50 torque split (and no low range). To withstand the Tesla motor's 450 hp and 325 lb-ft of torque, the SUV's original axles are upgraded with GBR Utah limited-slip differentials, Ashcroft half-shafts, and reinforced driveshafts from Tom Woods/Quadratec. Tesla battery modules are repackaged in two boxes, a big one that goes in the engine compartment and a smaller one that mounts inside the cargo area, the battery cooling system rides beneath the rear of the chassis. Together, these battery modules amount to 110 kWh of capacity. Charging is via a standard CCS Level 2 charging plug located behind the fuel-filler door. Sorry, there's no Tesla Supercharging or DC fast charging. This drivetrain swap adds about 1,400 pounds (6,400 total), much of it in the rear, so to bolster the GVW rating and achieve the proper ride height and body attitude, ECD puts the old Range Rover on air springs. Other chassis modifications include a switch to rear brake calipers that incorporate an electric parking brake—a major upgrade over the rear-driveshaft-mounted drum brake—and, to clear the front battery box, replacing the original hydraulic steering unit with one from a P38 Range Rover (1994-2001) that's powered by an electric pump.

description: This stunning AA Yellow 1995 Defender 90 NAS (North American Specification) has been subjected to a fastidious restoration and is reflecting less than 650 miles since completion. Come take this beauty for a test drive today! Land Rover supplied the Defender 90 NAS to North America for just three years, (1994, 1995 and 1997) in very low volumes. This example is number 2,413 produced and is powered by the venerable 3.9L naturally aspirated V8 engine sourced from the Rover Group and paired it with the 5-speed R-380 manual transmission. Initially, the Defender 90 was only available as a soft-top with a structural roll cage, but a later version was offered with a unique, removable, fiber-glass roof...this example is one which was supplied with this removable hardtop roof, (whilst still retaining the structural roll cage).This stunning example underwent a complete and professional restoration prior to our purchase in early-2021 to a very high level of attention to detail throughout. Almost everything has been replaced or refinished, including new paint and a new drive train, which includes a 3.9-liter 8-cylinder replacement factory engine, rebuilt original heads, new 5-speed manual transmission and a new transfer case. The radiator has been re-cored with an air conditioning system overhaul, including new hoses, compressor, condenser and blower. Custom thermal wrap covers the new intake hose and thermal sleeves cover the spark plugs. The new suspension includes 2-inch Terrafirma shocks, springs, steering stabilizer, BFGoodrich AT tires and new steel braided brake lines. The under body has been sprayed, headers and exhaust system have been painted, and the differentials, suspension and brake components refinished. The engine compartment has been customized with premium loom covering all wires and hoses, hood insulation pad and a custom polished radiator overflow reservoir. The interior has been redone to present as new and includes Dynamat insulation, new Exmoor Trim carpeting and mats, Land Rover rubber floor mats, Rovers North door panels and new shift boots. All gauges, knobs, steering column switches, rearview mirror, various pieces of dash (dash top, lower dash finishing trim) have also been replaced with new components and the dash recess was repainted. The original cubby was replaced with a larger, lockable metal cubby. The exterior features many custom details. Flat black textured paint has been applied to the roll bar, brush bar, running boards, fender flares, metal plate body protection, headlight surrounds and LED running light/turn signal bases. The headlights have been replaced with premium LED units, and all door hinges have been painted flat black to match the trim. The windshield and door seals are new as well.Galpin Land Rover has continued all maintenance whilst being a show car in our new showroom.PLEASE NOTE Due to the odometer being replaced during the restoration process, this vehicle is being offered for sale with True Mileage Unknown.

This beast of a truck is not just about getting from point A to point B, it's about doing it with style and performance. With its bold black exterior and alloy wheels, this Silverado demands attention wherever it goes. Slip inside the spacious cabin and grip the leather steering wheel as you take control and unleash the beast within. description: This used 2020 Toyota Sienna stands out as a versatile and well-equipped passenger van, perfect for families or anyone needing spacious, reliable transportation. With just under 88,000 miles, this Midnight Black Metallic beauty combines practicality with advanced features that elevate the driving experience. Its 3.5-liter V6 engine delivers a robust 296 horsepower, ensuring confident performance, while the 8-speed automatic transmission offers smooth shifts. The FWD layout enhances handling and efficiency, with an impressive 19 mpg city and 26 mpg highway. Inside, the gray interior offers comfort and convenience, complemented by a sunroof/moonroof and third-row seating. Modern amenities include adaptive cruise control, Apple CarPlay, blind spot monitor, Bluetooth, collision warning, cross traffic alert, heated seats, keyless entry, lane keep assist, push start, rear A/C, satellite radio readiness, and a Wifi hotspot, making every journey enjoyable and connected. This used Toyota Sienna combines safety, comfort, and cutting-edge technology to meet the demands of today's drivers. Its safety features include knee airbags for the driver and active head restraints for both front occupants, providing essential protection in the event of a collision. The van is equipped with four-wheel ABS to enhance braking stability and anti-lockout power door locks for added security. Auto-locking door locks ensure the vehicle remains secure when parked, giving peace of mind to owners. These safety features work together to create a secure environment for all passengers, making this used Sienna a smart choice for families prioritizing safety without sacrificing comfort or convenience. 2020 Toyota Sienna Safety and Security Features The safety and security of this used Sienna are reinforced by essential features such as knee airbags for the driver and active head restraints for both front occupants, which help minimize injury in a crash. The vehicle is equipped with four-wheel ABS, providing superior braking control under varied road conditions. Power door locks include anti-lockout functionality, preventing accidental lock-ins, while auto-locking features enhance security once the vehicle is in motion. These safety elements work seamlessly to protect occupants and provide peace of mind during every trip. 2020 Toyota Sienna Entertainment and Technology Features On the technology front, this used Sienna offers compatibility with Toyota Connected Services, allowing seamless integration with smart device apps for remote start, vehicle tracking, and more. Hands-free phone call integration, voice-operated radio, and a 7-inch touchscreen infotainment display make accessing entertainment and communication simple and safe. The HD radio and real-time traffic navigation keep drivers informed and entertained, while electronic messaging assistance with read and voice-operated functions ensures drivers stay connected without distraction. description:
Discover the pinnacle of luxury and performance in the 2022 Porsche Cayenne Platinum Edition. This stunning SUV is a true masterpiece, blending cutting-edge technology, unparalleled comfort, and the iconic Porsche driving experience.

Boasting an impressive array of features, this Cayenne Platinum Edition is a testament to Porsche's commitment to excellence. Key highlights include:

• Certified by Carfax - No Accidents, Certified by Carfax - One Owner
• Android Auto/Apple Car Play, Backup Camera, Bluetooth Hands Free Calling
• Alloy Wheels, Leather, Sunroof
• 14-Way Power Seats w/Memory Package, Premium Package Plus, Towing Package w/o Hitch Ball
• Navigation System, 4-Zone Climate Control, Front dual zone A/C, Heated Front & Rear Seats, Porsche Communication Management, Remote keyless entry, Traction control, ABS brakes, Low tire pressure warning, Power Liftgate, Electronic Stability Control, Heated door mirrors, LED-Matrix Headlights w/PDLS+, Illuminated entry, Lane Change Assist (LCA), Front Seat Ventilation, Heated front seats, Leather Seat Trim, Alloy wheels, Wheels: 21" RS Spyder Design in Satin Platinum

Powered by a robust 3.0L V6 engine and equipped with an 8-Speed Automatic with Tiptronic and All-Wheel Drive, this Cayenne delivers exceptional performance and handling. With an EPA-estimated 19 MPG in the city and 23 MPG on the highway, it offers a captivating blend of power and efficiency.

Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by a luxurious and meticulously crafted interior that exudes Porsche's renowned attention to detail. The Platinum Edition's premium amenities, including the Panoramic Sunroof and Heated Front and Rear Seats, ensure a truly indulgent driving experience.

description: Looking for a versatile and reliable used SUV that blends style, comfort, and modern technology? This 2016 Chevrolet Trax LT offers an exceptional driving experience with its sleek Champagne Silver Metallic exterior and Jet Black interior. With just over 95,900 miles, this well-maintained vehicle is built for city commuting and weekend adventures alike. Powered by a fuel-efficient 1.4-liter turbocharged four-cylinder engine, it produces 138 horsepower and 148 lb-ft of torque, ensuring a lively yet economical drive. The 6-speed automatic transmission and front-wheel-drive system provide smooth handling, making every trip enjoyable. Inside, you'll find seating for five with ample space, complemented by features like a backup camera, Bluetooth connectivity, premium audio, satellite radio readiness, and a WiFi hotspot—perfect for staying connected on the go. This Chevrolet Trax LT is equipped with a suite of safety features designed to give you peace of mind. Dual front knee airbags and four-wheel ABS contribute to enhanced protection in the event of a collision, while cornering brake control helps maintain stability during turns. The vehicle also features auto-locking power door locks, adding an extra layer of security when parked or driving. These advanced safety systems work together to ensure every journey is as secure as it is comfortable, making this SUV an excellent choice for families or individuals seeking reliability and peace of mind. 2016 Chevrolet Trax Safety and Security Features This model prioritizes safety with dual front knee airbags and four-wheel anti-lock braking system (ABS), providing vital protection for all occupants. Cornering brake control enhances stability during sharp turns, reducing the risk of skidding. Additionally, the vehicle features auto-locking power door locks, which automatically secure the doors when driving, adding an extra layer of security whether you're parked or on the move. 2016 Chevrolet Trax Entertainment and Technology Features Entertainment and connectivity are at the forefront of this Chevrolet Trax LT. It boasts a voice-operated radio system complemented by a 7-inch touch screen display, offering intuitive access to music, navigation, and more. The infotainment system also supports internet radio apps like Pandora and Stitcher, ensuring a variety of listening options. With six speakers, sound quality is crisp and immersive. For added convenience, the vehicle includes auxiliary audio inputs for USB and iPod/iPhone devices, along with electronic messaging assistance that is both read and voice-operated, helping you stay connected safely while on the road. This crew cab pickup combines advanced safety and convenience features with bold style. Enjoy premium comfort with leather-trimmed upholstery, heated and ventilated front seats, a heated steering wheel, and a power glass moonroof. Stay connected with a 10.25-inch touchscreen infotainment system, navigation with over-the-air updates, Apple CarPlay, and Android Auto. Power comes from a robust 2.5L Turbo I4 engine paired with an 8-speed double clutch transmission and on-demand AWD for confident handling in all conditions. The hard pickup tonneau cover, in-bed storage, and power locking/open tailgate make this SANTA CRUZ as practical as it is stylish. With 16,881 miles, this well-equipped Limited is ready for your next adventure.Certified Pre-Owned

2020 Mercedes-Benz GLE 350 4MATIC – Luxury, Performance, and Safety in One SUV

description: Experience power, luxury, and unmatched space with this Black 2023 GMC Yukon XL 4x4 AT4. Built for family adventures and executive comfort, it features the commanding EcoTec3 5.3L V8 engine and a 10-speed shiftable automatic transmission, delivering smooth performance on any terrain. The advanced 4x4 system and Hill Descent Assist ensure confidence in all conditions. Inside, you'll find Second Row Bucket seats with Power Release, heated and ventilated front seats, a heated steering wheel, and a Power Panoramic Moonroof for an elevated driving experience. Enjoy cutting-edge technology with a 10.2-inch GMC Infotainment System, wireless Apple CarPlay/Android Auto, Bose premium sound, wireless charging, and built-in navigation. Stay safe with Front Automatic Emergency Braking, Lane Keeping Assist, Blind Spot Monitoring, Rear Cross Traffic Alert, and a full suite of smart device integrations like OnStar and Amazon Alexa. The hands-free Power Liftgate, black running boards, and massive cargo space make every trip convenient. Don't miss out on this blend of rugged capability and modern luxury-test drive today!

description:
Good to go, our Accident Free, One Owner, Certified Pre-Owned 2025 Ford Bronco Badlands 4 Door 4X4 is built for extreme excitement in Velocity Blue Metallic! Motivated by a TurboCharged 2.7 Liter EcoBoost V6 delivering 330hp to a 10 Speed Automatic transmission for adventure-friendly performance. An upgraded HOSS 2.0 suspension with locking axles lets you dominate in the dirt, and this Four Wheel Drive SUV can achieve nearly 21mpg on the highway. Aggressive and expressive, our Bronco boasts LED lighting, a powder-coated steel front bumper, rock rails, bash plates, alloy wheels, and a removable body color hard top/doors for open-air exhilaration on your command!

Our Badlands cabin is smartly equipped for exploring your world with heated marine-grade front seats, a heated leather steering wheel, dual-zone automatic climate control, keyless access/ignition, and a multi-screen infotainment system. It features a 12-inch driver display and 12-inch touchscreen to support WiFi compatibility, connected navigation compatibility, wireless Android Auto®/Apple CarPlay®, Bluetooth®, voice recognition, and seven-speaker audio.

Ford helps seal the deal with lane-keeping assistance, automatic braking, blind-spot monitoring, forward collision warning, a rearview camera, hill start assistance, trailer sway control, tire pressure monitoring, stability/traction control, and more. You can get ready to go wild in our Bronco Badlands! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Corwin Ford Tri-City Test Drive Towards Ownership!

Discover the Rugged Versatility of the 2024 Ford Bronco Sport Badlands

Elevate your adventures with the 2024 Ford Bronco Sport Badlands, a true off-road champion that blends exceptional capability with refined style. This remarkable SUV is ready to conquer any terrain, from the urban jungle to the untamed wilderness, all while providing the comfort and convenience you demand.

• Equipped with the powerful EcoBoost 2.0L I4 GTDi DOHC Turbocharged VCT engine, delivering an exhilarating driving experience
• Enjoy the confidence of 4-Wheel Drive and the precision of the 8-Speed Automatic transmission
• Impressive fuel efficiency, with 21 MPG in the city and 26 MPG on the highway

Elevate your driving experience with the following premium features:

• SYNC 3 Communications & Entertainment System
• Automatic temperature control
• Power driver seat
• Remote keyless entry
• Four-wheel independent suspension
• Electronic Stability Control
• Auto High-beam Headlights
• Heated door mirrors

The Bronco Sport Badlands is more than just a capable off-road companion – it's a reflection of your adventurous spirit. Designed to tackle the toughest terrain with confidence, this SUV offers the perfect blend of rugged performance and refined comfort.

Discover the thrill of the open road and the freedom of the great outdoors with the 2024 Ford Bronco Sport Badlands. Experience the perfect balance of power, versatility, and style that will elevate your driving experience to new heights.

Don't settle for ordinary – embrace the extraordinary with the 2024 Ford Bronco Sport Badlands. Schedule a test drive today and let this remarkable SUV captivate your senses and inspire your next adventure.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with the captivating 2025 Volkswagen Atlas 2.0T Peak Edition. This exceptional SUV offers a perfect blend of power, style, and advanced technology, making it the ultimate companion for your adventures.

Boasting a robust 2.0L TSI engine paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission and all-wheel drive, the Atlas 2.0T Peak Edition delivers an exceptional performance that will leave you in awe. Enjoy the convenience of features like:

• Panoramic power moonroof
• Heated and ventilated front seats
• Heated steering wheel
• Hands-free power liftgate
• Surround-view camera system
• Adaptive cruise control
• Blind spot monitoring with rear cross-traffic alert

The Atlas 2.0T Peak Edition's sleek exterior is complemented by its spacious and well-appointed interior, offering seating for up to seven passengers. Indulge in the luxurious perforated V-Tex leatherette seating surfaces and bask in the natural light from the panoramic moonroof, creating a truly exceptional driving environment.

Engineered with your safety in mind, the Atlas 2.0T Peak Edition is equipped with a suite of advanced driver assistance features, including forward collision warning, automatic emergency braking, and lane-keeping assist. These cutting-edge technologies work together to provide you and your loved ones with the utmost protection on the road.

Boasting an impressive EPA-estimated fuel economy of 18 MPG in the city and 25 MPG on the highway, the Atlas 2.0T Peak Edition strikes the perfect balance between power and efficiency, ensuring you can conquer your daily commute and weekend adventures with ease.

Experience the ultimate in versatility, comfort, and performance with the 2025 Volkswagen Atlas 2.0T Peak Edition. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional SUV can elevate your driving experience. We're confident you'll be captivated by its unparalleled blend of style, technology, and capability.

Active owners love our Accident Free 2022 BMW X3 xDrive30i for its sporty performance and upscale details in Jet Black! Powered by a TurboCharged 2.0 Liter TwinPower 4 Cylinder offering 248hp to an 8 Speed Automatic transmission engineered for athletic action. You can also enjoy agile handling in this All Wheel Drive SUV, which can go from town to trail while scoring nearly 28mpg on the highway. A classic BMW grille grabs attention at first glance and complements LED lighting, a power tailgate, chrome-tipped exhaust, alloy wheels, sunroof, and satin aluminum roof rails. It's a sophisticated look that says you control the road!

Our xDrive30i cabin is tailored for confident travel with competitive advantages like SensaTec power heated front sport seats, a folding back row, a leather-wrapped heated sport steering wheel, automatic dual-zone climate control, Galvanic controls, and genuine wood accents. Exclusive BMW technologies include a 10.25 infotainment display, full-color navigation, WiFi compatibility, Apple CarPlay®, Android Auto®, Bluetooth®, and a HiFi sound system with SiriusXM compatibility.

Intelligent safety comes into focus with BMW's automatic emergency braking, forward collision warning, rearview camera, lane-departure warning, rear cross-traffic alert, blind-spot monitoring, and more! It's no wonder so many owners prefer our X3 xDrive30i! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Corwin Ford Tri-City Test Drive Towards Ownership!

Elevate your driving experience with this stunning 2023 Toyota Highlander Limited. Boasting a powerful 2.4L turbocharged engine, advanced all-wheel drive, and an impressive array of premium features, this SUV is the perfect blend of performance, capability, and luxury.

• Navigation System
• 12.3" Toyota Audio Multimedia with JBL Premium Sound
• Automatic Temperature Control
• Heated and Ventilated Front Seats
• Power Liftgate
• Exterior Parking Camera Rear
• Active Cruise Control
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto

This Highlander Limited is more than just a capable SUV—it's a true technological marvel. The state-of-the-art infotainment system puts a wealth of connectivity and entertainment at your fingertips, while the advanced driver assistance features, such as the Automatic High-Beam Headlights and Active Cruise Control, provide an extra layer of confidence and convenience on the road.

Slip behind the wheel and experience the refined power of the 2.4L turbocharged engine, which delivers an impressive 265 horsepower and 28 highway MPG. The smooth-shifting 8-speed automatic transmission and sophisticated all-wheel-drive system ensure exceptional handling and traction, no matter the weather or road conditions.

The Highlander's spacious and well-appointed interior is a true sanctuary on wheels. Sink into the plush, leather-trimmed seats and enjoy the convenience of dual-zone automatic climate control, a power driver's seat with memory function, and a panoramic moonroof that floods the cabin with natural light.

Whether you're transporting the family, embarking on a weekend adventure, or simply commuting in style, this 2023 Toyota Highlander Limited is the ultimate SUV companion. Experience the perfect blend of power, technology, and luxury by scheduling a test drive today.

At Hyundai of Venice, we use a market-based pricing technology with A.I. that compares our vehicles to similar ones nationwide—factoring in year, mileage, condition, and equipment. Every vehicle is pre-negotiated and priced below market value for a quick, hassle-free sale at a fair price. We also review our prices daily and adjust them based on live market conditions. Because of this data-driven approach and highly competitive pricing, our vehicles sell on average 20 days faster than comparable dealers!

Here and ready to impress, this 2025 Toyota Camry LE delivers the perfect balance of modern style, efficiency, and everyday comfort. Finished in sleek Celestial Silver Metallic, this front-wheel-drive sedan is powered by Toyota’s proven 2.5L 4-cylinder engine paired with a smooth eCVT, offering a refined driving experience with excellent fuel economy and confidence on the road.

Inside, the Camry LE features a clean, contemporary cabin trimmed in Boulder fabric upholstery, designed for comfort and ease of use. The intuitive Toyota Audio Multimedia system with an 8-inch touchscreen keeps you connected with Apple CarPlay, while a six-speaker sound system provides crisp, clear audio. Dual-zone automatic climate control, front bucket seats, and a tilt-and-telescoping steering wheel make every drive comfortable, whether it’s a daily commute or a longer trip.

Safety and driver-assist technology are front and center, with LED headlamps, lane assist, blind spot monitoring with rear traffic alert, adaptive cruise control, a rearview camera, traction control, and automatic high-beam headlights working together to provide added confidence behind the wheel. Alloy wheels and a clean, aerodynamic profile round out the Camry’s sharp, modern look.

This one-owner Camry includes the remainder of the factory warranty and has passed our comprehensive 127-point inspection. It also comes with a 5-day return and 30-day exchange for added peace of mind. Through our exclusive Fred Beans Auto Rewards Program, you’ll enjoy a $50 service gift certificate, free Pennsylvania state safety inspections, local merchant discounts, and the opportunity to earn up to $2,000 toward your next vehicle just by servicing with us. SPORT EXHAUST SYSTEM, DEVIATED STITCHING PACKAGE, SPORTDESIGN PACKAGE, AND MORE!

OVERVIEW
Here's a spec you don't want to miss. This range-topping 2025 Porsche 911 Turbo S represents the very best of Stuttgart engineering. At the rear is a 3.8L twin-turbo flat-six producing 640 horsepower and 590 lb-ft of torque, launching the Turbo S from 0-60 mph in a face-melting 2.6 seconds. Porsche's advanced all-wheel drive system and dynamic chassis control ensure that every ounce of power is translated into confident, razor-sharp control––allowing you to attack corners with confidence. Options are a-plenty, with active aero and a retractable rear wing working in tandem to manage airflow, and carbon ceramic brakes for fade-free stopping power. Exclusive Design taillights, a sport exhaust system, and LED Matrix Headlights illuminate the fact that this is no base spec Carrera. Inside, you'll find sports seats wrapped in black leather with Racing Yellow contrast stitching throughout. description: Experience luxury, power, and versatility with this White 2021 Ford Expedition Limited 4x4. Equipped with the robust EcoBoost 3.5L Twin Turbo V6 engine and a smooth 10-speed automatic transmission, this SUV is ready for any adventure. Enjoy premium features like leather-trimmed upholstery, heated and ventilated front seats, a heated steering wheel, and a Bang & Olufsen premium audio system. Stay connected with SYNC infotainment, Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, FordPass Connect, and a built-in Wi-Fi hotspot. Safety is a priority with adaptive cruise control, lane keeping assist, blind spot monitoring, front automatic emergency braking, and rear cross traffic alert. Convenience features include a power-operated liftgate, power-folding third-row seats, power retractable running boards, and a panoramic view via the rearview camera with washer. With seating for up to eight, tri-zone climate control, and up to 15 cupholders, this Expedition is perfect for families and road trips. Tow/haul mode, Class IV trailer hitch, and advanced 4WD ensure you're ready for anything. Don't miss this exceptional full-size SUV-schedule your test drive today!

More information about the 2017 Buick Cascada: There aren't many options these days when it comes to compact premium convertibles, but Buick is looking to change that. The Cascada outshines the BMW 228i convertible as well, easily besting it for standard features. With room for four adults to cruise top down in comfort, and with more trunk space than either the Mustang or Camaro convertible, the Cascada is a fascinating -- and potentially popular proposition from Buick. description: ********- MSRP OF $484,824 - ONE OWNER SINCE NEW - ASSETTO FIORANO PACK - $170,000 OF OPTIONAL CONTENT!!!**********This stunning 296 GTB was originally supplied by Ferrari of Houston and has had one-owner since new. The most recently service was completed by Ferrari of Fort Lauderdale in August 2025. The warranty start date was December 14th, 2022. Unveiled in June 2021, the 296 is Ferrari's first regular production model with a six-cylinder hybrid drive train that can produce a total of 819hp at 8,000rpm. The 2,992cc twin-turbo V6 engine is responsible for a total of 654hp with the electric only motor providing an additional 165hp. Torque is rated at 546lb/ft from the combined ICE and electric motors. A high-voltage accumulator positioned under the floor with an energy capacity of 7.45 kWh enables an electric only range of 16 miles. 0 to 62 mph (100km/h) is accomplished in just 2.9 seconds with a top speed recorded as being 205 mph.The 296 GTB replaced the prior mid-engine Ferrari F8 and joins the limited production SF90 in introducing a hybrid gas and electric joint power train.This beautiful example is finished in Grigio Scuro with Giallo Modena contrasting accents over a Nero Black interior and is optioned with almost $170,000 in optional extras. For a full breakdown of these optional items, the original window sticker is on display and is accompanied by the build plaque in the front trunk area.The Assetto Fiorano specification includes the following GT racing-derived upgrades:- Multimac shock absorbers optimized for the track.- High downforce carbon fiber appendages on the front bumper.- A lightweight Lexan rear screen.- Extensive lightweight carbon fiber materials both inside and out.More than just replacing elements of the 296 GTB, the Assetto Fiorano package completely redesigns some core aspects of the model, including a redesigned door panel (shedding over 26lbs) and a LaFerrari inspired active rear bumper designed to increase downforce by as much as 793lbs.Supplied with this 296 GTB are both keys, owners handbook package and the original window sticker.At Galpin Jaguar Land Rover of Van Nuys, our commitment to our customers produces one of the most valuable assets – and that's trust! We know you can't buy trust. You have to earn it! People have come to know that they can trust Galpin for the right selection, the right price, the right service and the latest innovations. That's why 92% of our customers are either repeat, reputational or referral. That's the Power of Trust! With over 75 years of automotive excellence we offer a commitment to an open, honest, and fair shopping experience. As an auto group we represent over 12 different brands from Volkswagen, Mazda, Honda, Lotus, Ford, Land Rover, Aston Martin, Lincoln, Polestar and Volvo. We have done a great amount of work to have the perfect selection of Pre-Owned vehicles and have researched hundreds of dealerships within a set radius to ensure we are competitively priced. Come on in today to check out our selection of Pre-Owned vehicles and experience exceptional service you can trust!

description:
This 2018 Toyota RAV4 XLE in Super White with a Gray interior has been through our 172-point presale inspection, which is the best you will find on the market, so youre not buying someone elses problem with a fresh air freshener. Its a 1-owner SUV with a good service history, and its been mainly serviced at Toyota dealerships, which is exactly what you want to see when youre shopping for a clean, dependable RAV4.

The best part, it has about 25,000 fewer miles than the average vehicle on the market within 500 miles, so youre getting the same proven Toyota reliability with a lot less wear and tear. Add in All-Wheel Drive and youve got a RAV4 that's ready for any weather, road trips, and everything in between without the drama.

Inside, you'll love the comfort and convenience features like dual-zone climate control, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, Bluetooth, USB port, and the smart key system. The fold-flat 2nd row seats make it easy to switch from passenger duty to cargo duty in seconds, whether you're hauling groceries, sports gear, or a suspicious amount of home improvement supplies.

For safety and confidence on the road, this RAV4 XLE comes with lane departure warning, blind spot monitor, rear cross traffic alert, and a backup camera. It also has a power tilt/slide moonroof for those days when you want fresh air without committing to a convertible lifestyle.

You'll also get navigation and SiriusXM, so you can find your way anywhere while listening to something better than road noise and regret.

And when you buy from us, you're part of something bigger: through our Keys 2 Empower program, after we sell 100 cars, we donate a vehicle to someone in need. So yes, you're getting a great SUV, and you're helping someone else get a fresh start too.

All of our cars receive a 172 point inspection*, a full professional detail, fresh oil, new cabin and engine air filters, two keys** when available, and a full tank of fuel so you start off strong.

At Mike's Car Store you get an easy buying experience with Chevy Dude, a well known YouTuber and the #1 car buying advocate online. His channel is packed with tips that help you beat the dealer and buy smarter. Buying A Car Doesn't Have To Suck, so check out our no haggle pricing. For availability or questions, call 812-940-6453. We are in Georgetown Indiana, about 15 minutes from Louisville.

We collect a 199.50 document fee on every sale. No surprise fees. Buyers are responsible for shipping, tax, tag, title, and license.

Philanthropy: For every 100 cars sold we donate a vehicle to someone who needs transportation. We also cover their taxes and title fees so they start with a clean slate.

We work hard to present accurate info, although listings might not show every feature. Inventory is subject to prior sale. Some photos are examples or stock photos. Vehicles might be off site or in transit. See the dealer for full details. Not responsible for typographical or pricing errors. Check out www.MikesCarStore.com for all photos and more.

If you read this far, take a quick break, grab a cheeseburger or a milkshake, then call us or stop by. If you swing by Chick Fil A, the owner takes a Spicy Chicken sandwich meal, one packet of mayo, one packet of mustard, large fries, four ketchup packets, and a large Arnold Palmer with no ice.

*The 172 point inspection gives a fair assessment at the time of inspection, without any warranty, express or implied. **Two keys provided when our supplier makes them available.

description:
**Popular Features**
• 3.5L PowerBoost Full-Hybrid V6
• 4WD with FX4 Off-Road Package
• Platinum Trim with Black Leather Interior
• 360-Degree Camera System
• Ford BlueCruise 1.0 Hands-Free Driving
• B&O Unleashed Premium Sound System
• Pro Trailer Backup Assist and Pro Trailer Hitch Assist
• Power Tailgate with Tailgate Step and Work Surface
• Twin Panel Moonroof

This **2023 Ford F-150 Platinum SuperCrew 4WD** brings together advanced hybrid performance, top-tier luxury, and serious capability in one of the most sophisticated trucks on the road. Finished in Avalanche Gray with a refined Black leather interior, this Platinum model sits at the top of the F-150 lineup. With a **Clean CARFAX, CARFAX One-Owner history**, and recent arrival status, it stands out as a premium, well-cared-for truck ready for work or adventure.

Power comes from the innovative 3.5L PowerBoost full-hybrid V6, paired with a smooth 10-speed automatic transmission and a capable 4WD system. This setup delivers impressive horsepower, strong towing capability, and improved efficiency. The FX4 Off-Road Package enhances capability with off-road tuned shocks, skid plates, hill descent control, rock crawl mode, and an electronic locking rear differential, giving you confidence on rough terrain or demanding job sites.

Inside, the Platinum trim surrounds you with upscale materials and cutting-edge technology. Heated and ventilated front seats, heated rear seats, a heated steering wheel, power-adjustable pedals with memory, and a twin panel moonroof create a first-class driving experience. The B&O Unleashed premium sound system delivers powerful, immersive audio, while SYNC 4 with enhanced voice recognition, navigation capability, and Ford BlueCruise 1.0 provide advanced connectivity and hands-free highway driving on compatible roads.

Trailering and utility features are equally impressive. The Bed Utility Package adds LED box lighting, BoxLink, a power tailgate, and a tailgate step with work surface. Pro Trailer Backup Assist, Pro Trailer Hitch Assist, an integrated trailer brake controller, and a Class IV trailer hitch make towing easier and more confident. A 360-degree camera system and Active Park Assist add everyday convenience and visibility.

With **76,158 miles**, this F-150 Platinum has proven its durability and capability. **This vehicle is not eligible for the Forever Warranty** due to mileage exceeding program requirements.

At **Step One Volkswagen of Ft. Walton Beach**, you will find a trusted hometown dealer committed to quality vehicles, customer satisfaction, and a friendly, stress-free local buying experience. Proudly serving Ft. Walton Beach, Florida, Step One Volkswagen makes it easy to shop with confidence and drive home happy.

**All Features and Equipment**

Discover the perfect blend of style, comfort, and technology in this stunning 2016 Nissan Murano SL. With its sleek exterior, spacious interior, and impressive performance, this certified pre-owned Murano is the ideal choice for the discerning driver.

Boasting a remarkable list of premium features, this Murano SL is a true standout in its class. Key highlights include:

• CERTIFIED BY CARFAX - ONE OWNER!
• REAR VIEW BACK-UP CAMERA!
• BLUETOOTH HANDS-FREE CALLING!
• NAVIGATION/GPS!
• HEATED SEATS!
• LEATHER SEATS!
• NON SMOKER!
• WHEELS: 18" 10-SPOKE BRIGHT PVD ALLOY

Powered by a robust 3.5L V6 DOHC engine paired with a smooth-shifting CVT with Xtronic, this Murano SL delivers an exceptional driving experience. With an impressive 21 city/28 highway MPG, you'll enjoy the perfect balance of power and efficiency.

Step inside and you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed cabin, featuring premium leather-appointed seats, a state-of-the-art navigation system, and a premium audio system with 11 speakers. The thoughtfully designed interior offers ample room for both passengers and cargo, ensuring your every journey is comfortable and convenient.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, and electronic stability control ensuring your peace of mind on the road.

Don't miss your chance to own this exceptional 2016 Nissan Murano SL. Schedule a test drive today and experience the perfect blend of style, comfort, and technology that this certified pre-owned Murano has to offer.

description:
Recent Arrival! This 2020 Lincoln Corsair Reserve comes equipped with a 2.0L 4-cylinder engine, an 8-speed automatic transmission, and all-wheel drive. Finished in Magnetic Gray, it has an excellent service history and includes Triton Certification, providing a 7-year/100,000-mile powertrain warranty along with a 12-month/12,000-mile comprehensive warranty. It also comes with a free first oil change, a 5-day return and 30-day exchange policy, and enrollment in our Auto Rewards Program.

This Corsair Reserve is well-equipped with lane assist, rear parking sensors, remote engine start, power-folding exterior mirrors, LED headlamps, Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, blind spot monitoring with rear traffic alert, ambient interior lighting, and a premium Revel 14-speaker audio system. Additional highlights include alloy wheels, auto high-beam headlights, an auto tilt-away steering wheel, automatic climate control, the Elements Package, dual-zone A/C, fully automatic headlights, heated rear seats, a heated steering wheel, heated and ventilated front seats, lane departure warning, a memory driver’s seat, built-in navigation, a power driver seat, a power liftgate, the panoramic Vista Roof, rain-sensing wipers, SiriusXM capability, the SYNC 3 infotainment system, and 19-inch Ultra Bright machined aluminum wheels. The windshield wiper de-icer adds convenience during cold-weather months.

For added confidence, every used vehicle we offer receives a 127-point inspection and includes our 5-day return and 30-day exchange guarantee (excluding As-Is vehicles). Our exclusive Auto Rewards Program adds even more value with a free first oil change, free Pennsylvania state safety inspections, local merchant discounts, and the opportunity to earn up to $2000 toward your next vehicle simply by servicing with Fred Beans. As we proudly say, our used cars are better because our reputation depends on it.

description: Please visit www.Survivor-Cars.com for additional photos, information, and a video. This vehicle is available for viewing in our Tampa Showroom by appointment only. Please call us to schedule an appointment. This fun clean little 2-seater drop top is a thrill to drive and has super low mileage. 12,628 actual miles on the clock and meticulously maintained, it has a lot of life to give. With a clean Carfax and 2-owner history, there is nothing to be afraid of with this little Chrysler sports car! This 2005 Chrysler Crossfire is a fuel-efficient sports car with plenty of pep and a long list of options. It is sure to please any car enthusiast. The 3.2-liter V6 engine puts down 215 horsepower with 229 lb-ft of torque and gets a very respectable 25 MPG on the highway. Being a front engine car with rear-wheel drive it feels sporty and fun. These cars are based very heavily on the Mercedes SLK, but can be had for a lot less money. Keep the top up and crank up the ice-cold A/C or drop that black soft top with the push of a button for an open air driving experience. The soft top folds nicely under a painted hard boot for a clean buttoned up look. Inside you get bucket seats, a center console, AM/FM/CD player, power windows, cruise control and tilt steering wheel. The seats are sporty yet comfortable and look great in charcoal leather. Options include: A/C, power top, power steering, power brakes, power windows, heated seats, AM/FM/CD player, leather interior, alloy wheels, radial tires, cruise control, and power locks. This car has everything you could ask for in terms of options, and youd be hard pressed to find a lower mileage, or cleaner example! This vehicle is available to view by appointment only. Please call the office to make an appointment. For additional information on this and our other classic and collectible cars for sale, please visit www.Survivor-Cars.com. For assistance, please call the office at (941) 845-4461, text our cell phones at (813) 358-8830, or email us at info@Survivor-Cars.com. If you are unable to come view the vehicle for yourself, we highly recommend you send in a third-party inspector on your behalf. We are located between Tampa and Sarasota. We are 90 minutes from Orlando and Fort Myers. *Potential purchaser understands it is their responsibility to verify condition and accuracy of information when purchasing from Survivor Classic Cars. It is the sole responsibility of the potential purchaser to inspect the vehicle, or have a third-party inspection performed on the vehicle before purchasing. description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, capability, and technology in this stunning 2021 Jeep Grand Cherokee Limited X. This exceptional SUV is ready to elevate your driving experience and take you on unforgettable adventures.

Boasting a sleek white exterior, this Grand Cherokee Limited X commands attention with its bold, distinctive design. Under the hood, the powerful 3.6L V6 24V VVT engine paired with an 8-Speed Automatic transmission delivers impressive performance and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 18 city/25 highway MPG.

This vehicle is packed with an impressive array of features:
• GPS Navigation
• HD Radio
• SiriusXM Satellite Radio
• Automatic temperature control
• Memory seat
• Power driver seat
• Power moonroof
• Power Liftgate
• ParkView Rear Back-Up Camera
• Bi-Xenon High-Intensity Discharge Headlamps
• Dual Dark Chrome Exhaust Tip
• LED Daytime Running Headlamps
• 8.4" Touchscreen Display
• Apple CarPlay
• Google Android Auto
• Heated front seats
• Leather Trimmed Seats
• Power passenger seat

The Limited X Package further enhances the Grand Cherokee's style and sophistication with features like a Sport Hood, Gloss Black Exterior Accents, Liquid Titanium Accents, and a Limited X Badge. The MOPAR Interior Protection Group adds premium cargo and floor mats to keep your vehicle looking its best.

description:
The 2025 Tesla Cybertruck Base arrives like an icon argued into existence a vehicle that refuses to blend in on principle. Its silhouette is less a conventional truck and more a folded plane: hard facets, razor edges and a stainlesssteel skin that seems engineered to be seen. Its architecture first, styling second a bold, polarizing statement that reads equally as sculpture and tool. Up close, the surfaces are unapologetically industrial, from a distance the Cybertrucks presence simplifies to a single, unforgettable intent: utility amplified by a futuristic aesthetic.

Driving it is a study in modern contradictions. The electric powertrain supplies instantaneous torque that makes urban maneuvers feel brisk and oddly effortless for something of its scale, the low battery mass stabilizes the platform in corners while lending a planted sense to highspeed cruising. Acceleration is immediate, the regenerative braking reshapes city driving into a onepedal rhythm for many drivers, and the overall sensation is of a heavy, capable machine moved with the immediacy of an EV. Handling favors stability and confidence over razorsharp agility this is a truck first, but one that deploys its propulsion with sportscar momentum when called upon.

Practicality is where the Cybertruck earns its keep. The bed is cavernous and multifunctional, the front storage compartment turns frunk space into usable volume, and the interior architecture prioritizes durability and simple utility. The cabin leans minimalist: a wide digital interface anchors the dash, controls are pared back, and the seating is focused on comfort and visibility rather than fussy luxury. Software is a defining feature overtheair updates, integrated connectivity and a suite of driver aids shape longterm ownership more than hardware spec sheets.

Of course, the Cybertrucks uncompromising design and size carry tradeoffs. Its geometry can make tight urban parking awkward, its look invites opinion, and ownership still leans on Teslas unique service and charging ecosystem. But for buyers who prize dramatic design, workready capability and an EV experience that feels like the future arriving early, the 2025 Cybertruck Base is a striking proposition: a durable, unorthodox truck that doubles as a cultural statement and a seriously capable daily tool.

  • Forward Collision and Cross Traffic Mitigation - Forward thinking with a side of safety. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. Or a vehicle runs a red light as you're approaching the intersection. That's when the Forward Collision and Cross Traffic Mitigation system comes to life. --When it senses an impending impact in front of you or on either side, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward Collision and Cross Traffic Mitigation is your doting eyes for crossing tees.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.

This 2022 Jeep Grand Cherokee L Overland is a true testament to the brand's commitment to exceptional craftsmanship and uncompromising performance. Experience the difference for yourself by scheduling a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by this remarkable SUV.

Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2024 Ram 1500 Classic SLT. This truck is more than just a workhorse, it's a true testament to engineering excellence, designed to provide you with unparalleled capability, comfort, and style.

• Triton Certified Classic Vehicle
• 3 Month/4,000 Mile Comprehensive Warranty
• 5 Day Return/30 Day Exchange
• Auto Reward Program
• Billet Silver Metallic Clearcoat
• Quick Order Package 29G SLT
• Radio: Uconnect 3 w/5" Display
• Integrated Voice Command w/Bluetooth

Under the hood, this Ram 1500 Classic SLT boasts a powerful 3.6L V6 24V VVT engine, mated to an 8-speed automatic transmission, delivering a responsive and efficient driving experience. With a fuel economy of 17 MPG in the city and 25 MPG on the highway, you'll enjoy the perfect balance of power and efficiency.

The exterior of this vehicle is adorned in a stunning Silver color, complemented by a host of premium features that elevate its presence on the road. From the chrome bumpers to the 17-inch aluminum wheels, every detail has been carefully crafted to ensure a bold and refined appearance.

Step inside the cabin, and you'll be greeted by a wealth of comfort and convenience features. The Cloth 40/20/40 Bench Seat provides ample space and support, while the Uconnect 3 infotainment system with a 5-inch display keeps you connected and entertained. The Remote Keyless Entry and Power Windows add to the overall ease of use, making this truck a pleasure to drive.

This 2024 Ram 1500 Classic SLT is more than just a vehicle, it's a testament to Triton's commitment to quality and craftsmanship. With its Triton Certified status, you can rest assured that this truck has been meticulously inspected and backed by a comprehensive warranty, giving you the peace of mind you deserve.

Don't miss the opportunity to experience the power, style, and versatility of this exceptional 2024 Ram 1500 Classic SLT. Visit our showroom today and let us help you discover the perfect truck to elevate your driving experience.

description:
This used 2023 BMW 3 Series 330i xDrive offers a perfect blend of luxury, performance, and cutting-edge technology. With just over 29,000 miles, this sedan presents an excellent opportunity to own a refined driving machine that combines sporty agility with everyday comfort. The striking Phytonic Blue Metallic exterior, complemented by a sophisticated Cognac interior, ensures you’ll turn heads wherever you go. Loaded with features like Apple CarPlay, a backup camera, Bluetooth connectivity, and a premium sunroof, this BMW is designed to enhance your driving experience while providing the reliability of a used vehicle. Its turbocharged 2.0-liter engine delivers 255 horsepower and 295 lb-ft of torque, making every drive dynamic and responsive. With advanced safety, entertainment, and performance features, this 3 Series is ready to elevate your daily commute and weekend adventures. This used BMW 3 Series 330i xDrive combines sporty performance with state-of-the-art technology, making it a compelling choice for discerning drivers. The vehicle’s all-wheel-drive system ensures confident handling in various conditions, while features like navigation with real-time traffic updates, satellite radio readiness, and a large 14.9-inch infotainment touchscreen keep you connected and entertained on the go. Inside, memory seats and rear A/C add convenience and comfort, and push start ignition simplifies your entry. The sleek exterior’s Phytonic Blue Metallic finish pairs beautifully with a refined interior in Cognac, creating a luxurious ambiance. With a balanced mix of power, style, and technology, this used BMW 3 Series promises an engaging and enjoyable driving experience. 2023 BMW 3 Series Safety and Security Features This used BMW 3 Series prioritizes safety with dual front knee airbags and four-wheel ABS to help protect occupants in the event of a collision. An interior motion sensor anti-theft system, combined with an anti-tow sensor, enhances security against theft. The vehicle also features emergency braking preparation, cornering brake control, and auto-locking power door locks to provide peace of mind. Brake drying and an electronic parking brake with auto-off further contribute to safe and reliable operation, making this sedan not only a pleasure to drive but also a secure choice for your daily transportation needs. 2023 BMW 3 Series Entertainment and Technology Features Equipped with a 14.9-inch infotainment touchscreen, this used BMW offers an intuitive interface for all your entertainment and navigation needs. Compatibility with BMW ConnectedDrive and Amazon Alexa allows seamless smart device integration, while voice-operated hands-free calling and messaging make staying connected safer and easier. The sound system features ten high-quality speakers, HD radio, and a touch screen display that delivers crisp audio and visual clarity. Real-time traffic data keeps you informed on the go, ensuring timely arrivals, and the vehicle’s advanced technology suite enhances convenience and entertainment at every turn. 2023 BMW 3 Series Performance Features Performance is at the heart of this used BMW 3 Series 330i xDrive, with auto start/stop technology that enhances fuel efficiency without sacrificing power. Its full-time all-wheel-drive system ensures optimal traction and handling in all driving conditions. Whether navigating city streets or open highways, this sedan offers a balanced mix of sporty agility and stability, making every drive engaging and confident. The combination of advanced performance features and a refined chassis makes this used BMW a standout choice for drivers seeking excitement and reliability.

Experience unmatched capability and premium comfort with the 2020 GMC Sierra 2500HD Denali. At our dealership, we are committed to delivering the highest quality and cleanliness with every used vehicle we sell. Each car undergoes an extensive reconditioning process to ensure it meets our rigorous standards. Beyond cleaning, our certified technicians conduct a thorough inspection and service, addressing routine maintenance such as oil changes, brake checks, tire rotations, and any necessary repairs to ensure optimal performance. This comprehensive approach ensures that every customer drives off with a vehicle that looks impeccable, runs smoothly, and offers the safety and reliability they deserve.

description:
Discover the ultimate work-hard, play-hard companion in this stunning 2021 GMC Sierra 1500 SLT. Meticulously maintained and ready to take on any task, this powerful truck is a true force to be reckoned with.

Boasting an impressive array of premium features, this Sierra 1500 SLT is engineered to exceed your expectations. Highlights include:

• Great Service History
• 3 Month/4,000 Mile Comprehensive Warranty
• TEXAS EDITION SLT PREMIUM PACKAGE
• X31 OFF-ROAD PACKAGE

Equipped with the robust EcoTec3 5.3L V8 engine and 4WD, this Sierra 1500 delivers exceptional performance and capability. Enjoy the confidence of hill descent control, skid plates, and all-terrain tires, whether you're tackling the job site or exploring the great outdoors.

Step inside and experience the unparalleled comfort and convenience of this well-appointed truck. Indulge in heated and ventilated front seats, a heated steering wheel, and a power-sliding rear window. Stay connected with the premium GMC Infotainment System, 4G LTE Wi-Fi, and a host of advanced safety and driver-assist technologies.

Designed to handle the demands of your active lifestyle, the Sierra 1500 SLT boasts a versatile cargo bed with a 120-volt power outlet, integrated trailer brake controller, and ProGrade Trailering System. Whether you're hauling heavy loads or towing your weekend toys, this truck is up for the challenge.

Elevate your driving experience and make a lasting impression with the bold, distinctive styling of the Sierra 1500 SLT. The Cardinal Red exterior, chrome accents, and 20-inch polished aluminum wheels exude confidence and sophistication.

Don't miss your chance to own this exceptional 2021 GMC Sierra 1500 SLT. Schedule a test drive today and discover the perfect blend of power, capability, and premium features that will transform the way you work and play.

description:
Why BUY from Jacobs Motors? When you choose this Championship White 2019 Honda Civic Type R Touring with 55,533 miles, you are not just buying a used vehicle - you are investing in quality, reliability and peace of mind. Our clientele depend on us for Transparent Pricing, Convenience and, most importantly, Customer FIRST Service! What this vehicle includes: Convenience
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
Safety and Security
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • Voice activated integrated navigation system - A to B made easy! Whether it's an errand or a road trip, the voice activated integrated navigation system will guide you to your destination. No more bulky, impossible-to-fold maps, and no more stopping to ask for directions. Just tell it where you want to go, and the voice activated integrated navigation system shows you the right way.
CHAMPIONSHIP WHITE, BLACK/RED, SUEDE-EFFECT FABRIC SEATING SURFACES W/TYPE R LOGO Come on in to Jacobs Motors today at 3230 14th St W Bradenton FL 34205 or call to schedule a test drive!

Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay/Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.
